20this%20year.%20%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BThese%20declines%20were%20attributable%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20rising%20interest%20rates%2C%20including%20lower%20existing%20home%20sales%20and%20mortgage%20refinancing%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Berkshire%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cu%3EManufacturing%3A%20consumer%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%20-%20revenues%20fell%20by%202%25%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20and%2013%25%20in%20the%20nine%20months%20to%20September.%20%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20declines%20reflected%20lower%20revenues%20at%20Forest%20River%20and%20nearly%20all%20of%20our%20apparel%20and%20footwear%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Berkshire%20said.%20Forest%20River's%20revenues%20fell%2017%25%20last%20quarter%20as%20sales%20volumes%20of%20recreational%20vehicles%20were%20hit%20by%20%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3Brising%20interest%20rates%2C%20inflation%20and%20other%20macroeconomic%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Meanwhile%2C%20apparel%20revenues%20slumped%20by%2015%25%20in%20the%20first%20nine%20months%20of%20this%20year%20due%20to%20%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3Blower%20volumes%20from%20declining%20customer%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cu%3EManufacturing%3A%20building%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%20-%20revenues%20fell%20by%2011%25%20and%20pre-tax%20earnings%20slid%20by%206%25%20last%20quarter.%20Clayton%20Homes'%20revenue%20from%20home%20sales%20tumbled%2017%25%20in%20the%20nine%20months%20ended%20September.%20Revenue%20from%20Berkshire's%20other%20building-products%20businesses%20dropped%20by%2011%25%20over%20the%20same%20period.%20%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3EThe%20effects%20of%20significant%20increases%20in%20home%20mortgage%20interest%20rates%20in%20the%20US%20over%20the%20past%20year%20has%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eslowed%20demand%20for%20our%20homebuilding%20businesses%20and%20our%20other%20building%20products%20businesses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Berkshire%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cu%3ERetailing%3C%2Fu%3E%20revenues%20rose%2