20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525996c6561dd877e766bcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENon-iPhone%20users%20can%20be%20singled%20out%20by%20the%20green%20text%20bubble.%3Cp%3EEgoitz%20Bengoetxea%20Iguaran%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20signed%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20EU%20asking%20for%20iMessage%20to%20be%20made%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bcore%20platform%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnder%20the%20bloc's%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%2C%20that%20would%20require%20Apple%20to%20make%20it%20compatible%20with%20other%20phones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20green%20text%20bubble%20currently%20singles%20out%20non-iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20and%20several%20telecom%20companies%20are%20asking%20European%20regulators%20to%20require%20that%20Apple's%20iMessage%20is%20made%20compatible%20with%20other%20phones%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fec2ec699-a91c-4389-b1a9-ae06dca836d5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20make%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-apple-imessage-iphones-android-green-blue-bubbles-peer-pressure-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20text%20bubbles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20single%20out%20non-iPhone%20users%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FT%2C%20Google%20and%20the%20other%20signatories%20want%20iMessage%20to%20be%20designated%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcore%20platform%20service%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20European%20Union's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-and-meta-among-6-gatekeepers-face-eu-competition-rules-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20Markets%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DMA%20is%20a%20major%20piece%20of%20legislation%20that%20aims%20to%20give%20more%20choice%20to%20users%20by%20setting