ff%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20designation%20because%20%26quot%3Benriched%20messaging%26quot%3B%20is%20only%20available%20between%20Apple%20users%2C%20per%20the%20FT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20and%20Google%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Apple%20spokesperson%20pointed%20the%20FT%20to%20an%20earlier%20statement%20which%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20today%20have%20access%20to%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20messaging%20apps%2C%20and%20often%20use%20many%20at%20once%2C%20which%20reflects%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20switch%20between%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20look%20forward%20to%20explaining%20to%20the%20commission%20why%20iMessage%20is%20outside%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20DMA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-asks-regulators-to-make-imessage-compatible-with-android-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699527665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654cb5e7b788914e555316c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-asks-regulators-to-make-imessage-compatible-with-android-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20and%20other%20telecoms%20companies%20asked%20the%20EU%20to%20make%20iMessage%20a%20%26quot%3Bcore%20platform%20service%26quot%3B%20under%20a%20law%20that%20could%20make%20it%20compatible%20with%20Android.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40insider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-asks-regulators-to-make-imessage-compatible-with-android-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20New%20Beatles%20Song%20%E2%80%98Now%20and%20Then%E2%80%99%20Uses%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploa