e%20our%20main%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20policymaker%2C%20I%20use%20my%20platform%20to%20fight%20against%20unrestricted%20tourism%2C%20counteract%20our%20current%20housing%20crisis%2C%20and%20campaign%20to%20protect%20our%20ocean%20and%20reef%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20my%20responsibility%20to%20advocate%20for%20my%20local%20community%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20big%20corporations%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20white-sand%20beaches%2C%20canoes%2C%20and%20divers%20and%20transformed%20our%20land%20into%20a%20shoreline%20of%20resorts%20like%20Waikiki%20in%20Oahu.%20They%20attempted%20to%20do%20this%20in%20Molokai%2C%20but%20the%20community%20fought%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20law%20school%20to%20become%20a%20policymaker%20because%20it%20was%20my%20kuleana%20%E2%80%94%20responsibility%20%E2%80%94%20to%20advocate%20for%20my%20community%20the%20same%20way%20my%20elders%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20work%20of%20Uncle%20Walter%20Ritte%2C%20a%20Native%20Hawaiian%20activist%20and%20educator%20who%20protested%20the%20military%20bombing%20practices%20on%20Kaho'olawe%20and%20won%20its%20eventual%20return%20to%20Native%20Hawaiian%20control%20from%20the%20US%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hold%20the%20County%20Council%20seat%20for%20the%20Molokai%20residency%20area%20and%20am%20part%20of%20the%20Efficiency%20Solutions%20and%20Circular%20Systems%20Committee%2C%20where%20I%20can%20discuss%20high-level%20budgets%20and%20allocation%20of%20resources%20to%20solve%20economic%20inequality%20that%20has%20been%20around%20for%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221989%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keani%20Rawlins%20Fernandez%2C%20Maui%20County%20Council%20Vice-Chair%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a4e843cc84b4dfafdac1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222693%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERawlins-Fernandez%20is%20a%20vice%20chair%20of%20the%20Maui%20County%20Council.%3Cp%3EKeani%20Rawlins-Fernandez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETourism%20has%20displaced%20Native%20Hawaiians%20by%20driving%20up%20costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20tourists%20in%20Hawaii%20is%20overwhelming%20the%20local%20population%20and%20threatening%20the%20islands'%20cultural%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENative%20Hawaiians%2C%20already%20displaced%20from%20their%20lands%20during%20colonization%2C%20are%20experiencing%20a%20housing%20crisis.%20When%20houses%20become%20available%2C%20they%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawaiipublicradio.org%2Flocal-news%2F2020-01-08%2Fnearly-a-quarter-of-hawaii-homes-are-purchased-by-out-of-state-buyers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20by%20tourists%20instead%20of%20locals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20buying%20our%20land%20as%20investment%20properties%2C%20so%20our%20Kanaka%20'%C5%8Ciwi%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0locals%20%E2%80%94%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F01%2F23%2Fhawaiians-cannot-afford-to-live-in-hawaii-las-vegas-drawing-natives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforced%20to%20move%20further%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20can't%20maintain%20their%20local%20traditions%20or%20routines.%20Basically%2C%20they%20need%20to%20start%20over%20and%20make%20a%20new%20place%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawaiibusiness.com%2Ftracking-hawaii-paychecks-minimum-wage-living-costs-inflation%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHousing%2520Prices%2520Outpace%2520Wages%2520for%2Cinflation%2520%25E2%2580%2593%2520increased%2520only%252039%2525.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecost%20of%20living%20has%20skyrocketed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20demand%20drives%20up%20real-estate%20prices.%20Residents%20of%20islands%20like%20Maui%20and%20Oahu%2C%20where%20tourism%20is%20at%20peak%20levels%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.hawaii.gov%2Fdbedt%2Feconomic%2Freports%2FNative_Hawaiians_in_Tourism_2021.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erely%20on%20resorts%20and%20hotels%20for%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20their%20livelihood.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID%2C%20there%20was%20no%20tourism%2C%20and%20their%20jobs%20were%20the%20first%20to%20go.%20My%20island%20in%20Molokai%20fared%20better%20because%20the%20model%20is%20to%20cater%20to%20local%20businesses%20and%20local%20patrons%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20can't%20commute%20easily%20because%20tourists%20are%20getting%20their%20sunset%20pictures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20large%20part%20of%20Hawaii's%20economy%20is%20reliant%20on%20tourism%2C%20but%20in%20popular%20tourist%20areas%2C%20overtourism%20is%20placing%20huge%20strains%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20environment%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0especially%20when%20the%20number%20of%20visitors%20exceeds%20the%20resident%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20famous%20sights%20like%20Waikiki%20Beach%20and%20Diamond%20Head%20on%20Oahu%20draw%20crowds%20of%20tourists%20for%20sunrise%20or%20sunset%20views.%20This%20clogs%20up%20our%20highways%20during%20the%20hours%20when%20locals%20are%20trying%20to%20commute%20or%20drop%20their%20kids%20off%20at%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20wants%20to%20create%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.civilbeat.org%2F2023%2F06%2Fthis-stretch-of-north-shore-highway-could-be-moving-inland-with-a-parking-lot-on-the-beach-side%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eparking%20spots%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20widen%20highways.%20Instead%2C%20people%20should%20consider%20group%20trolley%20systems%20like%20the%20ones%20in%20Zion%20National%20Park%20in%20Utah%2C%20which%20I%20recently%20visited%2C%20to%20manage%20tourists.%20This%20makes%20more%20sense%20than%20allowing%20tourists%20to%20rent%20their%20own%20car%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20their%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocals%20feel%20like%20their%20home%20is%20a%20theme%20park%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20can%20be%20dangerous%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20locals%20feel%20like%20their%20homes%20are%20treated%20like%20a%20theme%20park%20and%20there's%20no%20more%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20heard%20stories%20of%20tourists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2Fhawaii-volcano-kilauea-eruption-photos-fines-arrests%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etrespassing%20on%20properties%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20photo%20opportunities.%20But%20they%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20unlike%20television%20or%20social-media%20posts%2C%20this%20is%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20always%20safeguards%20and%20railings%20at%20places%20like%20our%20waterfalls%20or%20volcanoes.%20Tourists%20have%20passed%20away%20or%20become%20severely%20hurt.%20It%20puts%20our%20emergency%20responders%20at%20risk%20if%20tourists%20are%20trespassing%20in%20dangerous%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20beaches%20and%20reefs%20are%20being%20degraded%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20tourism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExcessive%20tourist%20activity%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fgrrlscientist%2F2023%2F01%2F16%2Ftourists-are-loving-hawaiis-coral-reefs-to-death%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20a%20major%20toll%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Hawaii's%20fragile%20island%20ecosystems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20natural%20sand%20dunes%20in%20Hawaii%20enable%20a%20cyclical%20restoration%20of%20the%20white-sand%20beaches.%20However%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20resorts%20and%20hotel%20chains%20on%20the%20dunes%20disrupts%20this%20cycle%2C%20preventing%20the%20beaches%20from%20replenishing%20lost%20sand.%20With%20the%20dunes%20unable%20to%20supply%20fresh%20sand%2C%20the%20beaches%20steadily%20erode%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20temporary%20seawalls%20being%20built%20in%20f