ised%20for%20Dhirendra%20Shastri%2C%20the%20chief%20priest%20of%20the%20Bageshwar%20Dham%2C%20at%20the%20parade%20ground%20in%20Dehradun.%20At%20the%20event%2C%20Hindutva%20leaders%20including%20Shastri%2C%20made%20hateful%20remarks%20targeting%20the%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20received%20little%20coverage%20and%20almost%20no%20outrage%20in%20the%20national%20media.%20Almost%20no%20Hindi%20channel%20reported%20on%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20speech%20and%20one%20channel%20reported%20it%20as%20the%20Godman%E2%80%99s%20advice%20to%20religious%20minorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20summary%20of%20the%20supposed%20%E2%80%98advice%E2%80%99%20that%20Shastri%20gave%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20a%20person%20is%20O%2B%2C%20can%20he%20accept%20another%20blood%20group%3F%E2%80%A6So%2C%20if%20the%20body%20can%E2%80%99t%20accept%20another%20blood%20group%20then%20how%20can%20we%20accept%20another%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereligion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20coming%20here%2C%20I%20was%20told%20that%20JCBs%20have%20been%20run%20over%20the%20lands%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20people%E2%80%9D.%20I%20replied%20that%E2%80%99s%20very%20good%E2%80%A6Right%20now%20Maharaj%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20also%20telling%20us%20how%20they%20capture%20land%20and%20cover%20it%20with%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echadar%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20CM%20should%20be%20who%20takes%20away%20the%20homes%20of%20those%20who%20say%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20Babur%E2%80%99s%20land.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20mosques%20to%20be%20made%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Only%20Ram%20temples%20should%20be%20constructed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShastri%20also%20compared%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20to%20ghosts%20and%20ghouls%20who%20can%20be%20shooed%20away%20by%20chanting%20the%20names%20of%20Hindu%20Gods%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShastri%20was%20received%20by%20CM%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20and%20even%20escorted%20to%20the%20stage.%20After%20Shastri%E2%80%99s%20address%2C%20Dhami%20described%20him%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cguardian%20of%20the%20Hindu%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20as%20one%20conveying%20the%20true%20identity%20of%20India%20to%20the%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20Shastri%2C%20Swami%20Darshan%20Bharti%20was%20also%20mentioned%20by%20Dhami%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharti%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20on%20the%20stage%2C%20had%20hit%20the%20headlines%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fas-tensions-run-high-in-purola-muslims-flee-uttarkashi-bjp-minority-wing-leaders-feel-betrayed%5C%22%3EMuslims%20were%20driven%20out%20of%20the%20Purola%20town%20and%20their%20businesses%20were%20targeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20being%20marked%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98X%E2%80%99%20sign.%20Later%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20the%20whole%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20charge%20was%20false.%20%E2%80%98Love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20bogey%20claiming%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20Muslims%20to%20convert%20Hindu%20brides.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharti%20is%20one%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20leaders%20from%20the%20state%20whose%20name%20regularly%20features%20in%20anti-Muslim%20hate%20videos.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%20to%20a%20local%20online%20portal%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20his%20speeches%20can%20incite%20people%2C%20to%20which%20he%20lamented%20that%20people%20do%20not%20get%20provoked%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20were%20actually%20getting%20provoked%20then%20the%20limbs%20of%20so%20many%20Muslims%20would%20have%20been%20chopped%20off%20till%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20heard%20saying.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharti%20was%20a%20prominent%20speaker%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-leaders-dharma-sansad-muslim-genocide%5C%22%3Einfamous%20Haridwar%20Dharam%20Sansad%20where%20calls%20for%20mass%20killings%20of%20Muslims%20were%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20at%20the%20Haridwar%20Dharma%20Sansad%2C%20Bharti%20spoke%20about%20%E2%80%9CIslamic%20activities%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Edevbhoomi%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20that%20even%20Aurangzeb%20had%20not%20managed%20to%20conquer%20the%20devbhoomi%20and%20claimed%20that%20its%20people%20have%20not%20allowed%20any%20mosque%20to%20be%20built%20there%20since%202015.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20mazar%20was%20allowed%20to%20be%20built..%20No%20madrasa%20was%20allowed%20to%20be%20built%E2%80%A6Remember%20this%20too%E2%80%A6Learn%20this%20from%20these%20poor%E2%80%A6I%20definitely%20wish%20to%20put%20to%20you%20people%20that%20only%20after%20saving%20that%20shrine%20of%20Hindu%20religion%20can%20we%20talk%20of%20a%20Hindu%20nation%E2%80%A6If%20India%20follows%20the%20path%20shown%20by%20Shankaracharya%20ji%2C%20then%20surely%20this%20saint%20will%20give%20you%20this%20knowledge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANINewsUP%2Fstatus%2F1673664704642789378%3Ft%3D2XMjDIeTNJQ7Sr5P36bT9A%26s%3D19%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Uttarakhand%20is%20suffering%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Cjihadis%20who%E2%80%99ve%20invaded%E2%80%9D%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20wave%20of%20Hindutva%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20start%20from%20Uttarakhand%20then%20the%20nation%20won%E2%80%99t%20become%20a%20Hindu%20state%E2%80%A6This%20country%20has%20to%20be%20made%20a%20Hindu%20rashtra%20and%20all%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Devbhoomi%20need%20to%20take%20this%20vow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlmost%20all%20Hindi%20newspapers%20had%20great%20things%20to%20say%20about%20the%20event.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20adjectives%20being%20used%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20the%20media%20are%3A%20vulgar%2C%20incendiary%2C%20misogynist%2C%20sexist%2C%20controversial%2C%20and%20bizarre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Uttarakhand%20high%20court%20have%20repeatedly%20questioned%20the%20state%20government%20for%20their%20inaction%20against%20hate%20speech%2C%20something%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20become%20so%20routine%20in%20the%20state%20that%20no%20media%20has%20even%20bothered%20to%20report%20about%20it%2C%20despite%20it%20happening%20in%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20warned%20that%20any%20delay%20in%20registering%20hate%20speech%20cases%20would%20be%20considered%20contempt%20of%20court%2C%20and%20described%20hate%20speech%20as%20a%20severe%20crime%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%20the%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699526529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09161001%2FF-G0PpOW4AAQ4mn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fpushkar-singh-dhami-nitish-kumar-media-hate-speech%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20an%20event%20attended%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20CM%2C%20priest%20Dhirendra%20Shastri%20made%20incendiary%20comments%20against%20Muslims.%20These%20found%20no%20mention%20on%20papers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fpushkar-singh-dhami-nitish-kumar-media-hate-speech%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22a