2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654a63e0b788914e5551a5c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20group%20chat%20has%20become%20the%20fulcrum%20of%20civilization%20and%20its%20discontents.%20In%20order%20to%20survive%20and%20thrive%20as%20humans%2C%20it's%20time%20for%20us%20to%20agree%20on%20group-chat%20etiquette.%3Cp%3EMin%20Heo%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENever%20start%20a%20group%20chat%20at%203%3A47%20in%20the%20morning.%C2%A0Never%20invite%20both%20your%20ex-lover%20and%20your%20dad%20to%20the%20same%20group%20chat.%20Never%20name%20a%20group%20chat%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20group%20chat%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20actually%20includes%20your%20ex-lover%20(who's%20also%20the%20CEO%20of%20one%20of%20your%20companies)%2C%20your%20dad%2C%20your%20general%20counsel%2C%20and%20nine%20of%20your%20top%20executives%2C%20and%20when%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20chat%20is%20to%20scramble%20to%20save%20face%20and%20funds%20as%20your%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20collapses%20amid%20the%20news%20that%20you%20may%20have%20stolen%20up%20to%20%2410%20billion%20from%20your%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20just%20three%20of%20many%20deadly%20sins%20of%20the%20group%20chat%20that%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20committed%20in%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20November%207%2C%202022.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20the%20panicked%20texts%20shared%20in%20that%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20group%20chat%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20other%20chats%20with%20cutesy%20names%20like%20%26quot%3BDonation%20Processing%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPeople%20of%20the%20House%26quot%3B%20(the%20presumably%20absolutely%20insufferable%20people%20living%20in%20Bankman-Fried's%20%2435%20million%20penthouse)%20%E2%80%94%20comprised%20some%20of%20the%20most%20damning%20evidence%20against%20him%20and%20helped%20lead%20to%20a%20swift%20guilty%20verdict%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjury-sam-bankman-fried-guilty-seven-counts-fraud-manhattan-trial-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseven%20counts%20of%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20may%20be%20the%20first%20person%20to%20serve%20up%20to%20110%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20doing%20so%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20person%20to%20perpetrate%20a%20group-chat%20faux%20pax.%20You%2C%20your%20friends%2C%20and%20your%20mom%20probably%20perpetrated%20several%20this%20morning.%20Worry%20not.%20Like%20any%20good%20group%20chat%2C%20this%20is%20a%20safe%20space%2C%20and%20I'm%20here%20to%20help%20you%20navigate%20these%20tricky%20currents.%20%E2%9D%A4%EF%B8%8F%E2%9D%A4%EF%B8%8F%E2%9D%A4%EF%B8%8F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20chat%20hasn't%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-dead-instagram-tiktok-bereal-replaced-group-chats-messaging-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebludgeoned%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20submission%2C%20siphoning%20off%20users%20and%20engagement%20from%20a%20barren%20Facebook%2C%20a%20boring%20Instagram%2C%20and%20the%20bilious%20and%20broken%20Twitter%20(I'm%20not%20calling%20it%20X).%20The%20group%20chat%20has%20become%20the%20fulcrum%20of%20civilization%20and%20its%20discontents.%20From%20planning%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20to%20the%20run%20on%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank%20to%20national-security%20leaks%2C%20from%20secret%20threads%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com%2Fculture%2Fcareer-politics%2Fa45459012%2Fdemocratic-women-governors-friendship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemocratic%20women%20governors%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Ftelegram-hamas-israel-conflict%2F%23intcid%3D_wired-verso-hp-trending_dfdf5d83-b27f-45e7-8815-a459b552d980_popular4-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas%20militants%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20tromboners%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fparenting%2F2023%2F10%2F30%2Fteen-group-texts-rules%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emiddle-school%3C%2Fa%3E%20marching%20band%2C%20the%20group%20chat%20is%20now%20the%20room%20where%20it%20happens%2C%20for%20better%20and%20worse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20struggling%20with%20the%20endlessly%20pinging%20ubiquity%20of%20the%20group%20chat.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.securedatarecovery.com%2Fblog%2Fgroup-messaging-feels-like-job%23Americans%25E2%2580%2599_group_messaging_habits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%201%2C005%20US%20adults%20found%20the%20average%20American%20spends%2026%20minutes%20a%20day%20reading%20and%20responding%20to%20group%20chats.%20Some%20two-thirds%20said%20they%20feel%20overwhelmed%20by%20them%2C%20and%2042%25%20say%20keeping%20up%20with%20them%20feels%20like%20a%20part-time%20job.%20%26quot%3BGroup%20Chat%20Culture%20Is%20Out%20of%20Control%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20article%20in%20The%20Atlantic%20decried%20in%20September.%20%26quot%3B57%20Messages%20in%20One%20Day.%20The%20Group%20Text%20Has%20Gone%20Off%20the%20Rails%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20headline%20in%20October.%20In%20early%20November%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Indonesia%20was%20reportedly%20suspected%20of%20stabbing%20and%20killing%20his%20friend%20after%20the%20friend%20removed%20him%20from%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20chat%20about%20motorcycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20like%20this.%20As%20a%20public%20proselytizer%20of%20group%20chats%20and%20all%20the%20chaos%20and%20high-stakes%2C%20potentially%20friendship-%2C%20career-%2C%20company-%2C%20and%20government-ending%20texts%20that%20come%20with%20them%2C%20I%20can't%20stand%20to%20see%20the%20name%20of%20group%20chats%20smeared%20and%20watch%20people%20make%20egregious%20chat%20gaffes%20any%20longer.%20A%20century%20ago%2C%20Emily%20Post%20tried%20to%20set%20order%20to%20the%20frenetic%20melting%20pot%20of%20a%20young%20American%20nation%20with%20her%20book%20%26quot%3BEtiquette%20in%20Society%2C%20in%20Business%2C%20in%20Politics%2C%20and%20at%20Home.%26quot%3B%20Well%2C%20society%2C%20business%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20home%20life%20have%20all%20entered%20the%20group%20chat.%20For%20us%20to%20survive%20and%20thrive%20as%20humans%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20agree%20on%20the%20Definitive%20Etiquette%20of%20the%20Group%20Chat.%20Set%20your%20phones%20to%20Do%20Not%20Disturb%20for%20the%20next%20few%20minutes.%20In%20advance%2C%20you're%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2057%20unread%20messages%20is%2C%20as%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20rails%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20I%20must%20be%20somewhere%20in%20the%20ravine%2C%20flipped%20over%2C%20and%20taking%20on%20water%20as%20I%20burst%20into%20flames.%20Fifty-seven%20messages%20(sincerest%20apologies%2C%20Ms.%20Post)%20can%20constitute%20one%20rigorous%20morning%20toilet%20session.%20Sometimes%20I%20come%20home%20to%2057%20unread%20messages%20after%20my%2020-minute%20round-trip%20drive%20to%20drop%20my%20daughter%20off%20at%20day%20care.%20In%20October%20alone%2C%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20unread%20counts%20from%20a%20single%20chat%20numbering%20in%20the%20hundreds%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20(a%20chat%20with%20several%20of%20my%20friends%20who%20don't%20have%20kids).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%20chat%2C%20some%20of%20my%20most%20active%20group%20chats%20include%20one%20with%20my%20high-school%20friends%2C%20another%20with%20college%20friends%2C%20and%20another%20with%20friends%20from%20the%20college%20I%20dropped%20out%20of.%20There's%20one%20with%20close%20friends%20living%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20who%20have%20kids%20the%20same%20age%20as%20mine%2C%20and%20another%20with%20close%20friends%20in%20Rome%20who%20have%20kids%20the%20same%20age%20as%20mine.%20One%20with%20my%20dad%20and%20sister%20and%20our%20spouses%2C%20and%20one%20with%20just%20my%20dad%20and%20sister.%20One%20with%20my%20old%20bandmates%20to%20trade%20jokes%20and%20reminisce%20about%20tours%20and%20records%20and%20shows%20of%20yore%2C%20and%20one%20with%20my%20current%20bandmates%20to%20trade%20jokes%20and%20discuss%20rehearsals%20and%20upcoming%20shows.%20There's%20one%20to%20piss%20and%20moan%20about%20the%20Mets%20(though%2C%20like%20the%20Amazins%2C%20that%20one%20is%20only%20active%20between%20April%20and%20July)%2C%20and%20one%20to%20piss%20and%20moan%20about%20the%20New%20York%20Giants%2C%20which%20is%20laden%20with%20more%20profanity%20and%20sadness%20than%20I%20am%20comfortable%20to%20admit%20publicly.%20There's%20one%20each%20for%20a%20pair%20of%20fantasy%20football%20leagues%20I%20play%20in%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20I%20have%20almost%20no%20interest%20in%20fantasy%20football%3B%20I'm%20mostly%20in%20the%20leagues%20for%20the%20group%20chats%20that%20come%20with%20them.%20There%20are%20others%2C%20of%20course.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20I%20think%20about%20it%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20two%20others%20are%20the%20only%20people%20I%20regularly%20text%20one-on-one%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ultimate%20appeal%20of%20group%20chats%20%E2%80%94%20their%20necessity%2C%20really%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20they've%20become%20the%20only%20social%20media%20that's%20actually%20social.%20It%20wasn't%20always%20this%20way.%20Social%20media%20was%20originally%20conceived%2C%20publicly%2C%20at%20least%2C%20to%20foster%20connection.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20once%20promised%20that%20Facebook%20would%20%26quot%3Bgive%20people%20the%20power%20to%20share%20and%20make%20the%20world%20more%20open%20and%20connected.%26quot%3B%20Twitter%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bserve%20the%20public%20conversation.%26quot%3B%20But%20connection%20has%20long%20since%20given%20way%20to%20the%20attention%20economy%20on%20most%20platforms%2C%20between%20thinking%20in%20terms%20of%20tweets%2C%20seeing%20the%20world%20for%20its%C2%A0%20'gramability%2C%20and%20slipping%20into%20the%20infinite%20scroll%20of%20TikTok.%20Group%20chats%20are%20now%20the%20rare%20place%20to%20gather%20that%20isn't%20gamified%20or%20monetized%2C%20where%20sharing%20the%20perfect%20meme%20to%20dunk%20on%20your%20friend's%20horrifying%20first%20date%20won't%20be%20drowned%20out%20by%20ads%20for%20Adidas%20and%20antidepressants%20and%20an%20unhinged%20rant%20from%20some%20blue-check%20neo-Nazi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20social%20media%20doubles%20down%20in%20what%20The%20New%20Yorker%20writer%20Hua%20Hsu%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2023%2F03%2F20%2Fwhat-conversation-can-do-for-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eage%20of%20the%20amygdala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20group%20chats%20give%20us%20the%20space%20to%20engage%20all%20the%20other%20parts%20of%20our%20brain%2C%20a%20chance%20to%20listen%20and%20be%20heard%20and%20engage%20in%20actual%20conversation%20and%20community-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20the%20micro-communities%20of%20group%20chats%20develop%20their%20own%20shorthand.%20There%20are%20jokes%20that%20reference%20this%20thing%20or%20that%20from%20years%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20texts%20ago%2C%20some%20note%20that%20has%20become%20part%20of%20the%20thread's%20shared%20vernacular.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20jokes%20can%20stretch%20a%20touch%20too%20far%2C%20seeping%20into%20the%20real%20world%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20when%20one%20of%20my%20group%20chats%20incorporated%20as%20an%20LLC%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Why%3F%20Because%20it%20was%20hilarious.%20At%20least%20it%20was%20to%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chats%20also%20codify%20their%20own%20social%20strata.%20There's%20the%20person%20who%20shares%20the%20best%20memes%3B%20the%20person%20who%20always%20takes%20the%20joke%20one%20text%20too%20far%3B%20the%20boomer%20who%20types%20in%20all%20caps%2C%20uses%20proper%20punctuation%2C%20and%20signs%20their%20name%20to%20the%20text.%20Me%3F%20I'm%20the%20guy%20who%20feels%20like%20he%20has%20to%20like%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eevery%20meme%20shared%20in%20our%20threads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroup%20chats%20can%20become%20overwhelming%2C%20of%20course%2C%20especially%20as%20they%20creep%20into%20other%20apps%20and%20%3Cem%3Eespecially%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20they%20often%20duplicate%20participants.%20But%20when%20you%20think%20of%20them%20as%20a%20conduit%20by%20which%20we%20stay%20connected%20to%20our%20favorite%20people%2C%20to%20laugh%20as%20though%20we%20were%20all%20crowded%20into%20a%20booth%20at%20the%20local%20bar%20together%2C%20or%20even%20to%20learn%20and%20develop%20relationships%20with%20people%20we%20don't%20know%20that%20well%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20hate%20on%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Not%20to%20mention%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20can%2C%20you%20know%2C%20just%20leave%20group%20chats%2C%20as%20my%20father%20often%20does%20from%20our%20family%20thread.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20for%20us%20all%20to%20embrace%20the%20ping.%20And%20if%20you%20can't%2C%20learn%20how%20to%20mute%20your%20phone%2C%20you%20Luddite.%20But%20like%20America's%20interstate%20system%20or%20the%20number%20of%20times%20you%20can%20wear%20jeans%20before%20washing%20them%2C%20there%20have%20to%20be%20rules.%20What%20was%20once%20the%20Wild%20West%20of%20interpersonal%20communication%20is%20now%20becoming%20the%20Tucson%20your%20parents%20are%20thinking%20of%20retiring%20to.%20And%20even%20Tucson%20has%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20rules%20have%20been%20crowdsourced%20from%20my%20own%20group%20chats.%20They%20work%20for%20any%20group.%20Follow%20them%20religiously%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20become%20the%20next%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried.%20Also%2C%20try%20and%20avoid%20creating%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20fake-money%20fraud%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%9A%A8The%20rules%20apply%20to%20consenting%20adults%20only.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20recent%20Washington%20Post%20story%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fparenting%2F2023%2F10%2F30%2Fteen-group-texts-rules%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunwritten%20rules%20of%20teen%20group%20chats%3C%2Fa%3E%20warns%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20say%20anything%20you%20wouldn't%20want%20screenshotted.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20sage%20advice%20for%20the%20social%20barbarism%20of%20high%20school.%20This%20is%20terrible%20advice%20for%20adults%2C%20and%2C%20if%20followed%2C%20would%20maybe%20keep%20you%20out%20of%20trouble%20but%20would%20definitively%20neuter%20the%20fun%20and%20intimacy%20of%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20official%20rules%20of%20the%20group%20chat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20The%20perfect%20group%20chat%20size%20is%20six%20people.%20Don't%20let%20it%20exceed%2012.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20chat%20is%20like%20a%20table%20at%20a%20restaurant.%20Six%20makes%20for%20freewheeling%20conversation%20over%20candlelight%20where%20everyone%20can%20feel%20like%20they%20have%20an%20equal%20stake.%20It%20also%20gives%20everyone%20a%20chance%20to%20step%20back%20if%20they're%20not%20feeling%20it%20that%20day.%20Beyond%20eight%2C%20chatter%20becomes%20more%20and%20more%20rowdy%2C%20performative%2C%20and%20splintered.%20Also%2C%20a%20group%20chat's%20vitality%20is%20inversely%20proportional%20to%20the%20number%20of%20lurkers%20in%20the%20chat%2C%20and%20more%20people%20always%20means%20more%20lurkers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Mute%20group%20chats%20with%20more%20than%2012%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20both%20your%20psyche%20and%20for%20the%20greater%20good.%20The%20texts%20aren't%20going%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Don't%20talk%20about%20the%20group%20chat%20outside%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20you%20should%20never%20comment%20on%20someone's%20Instagram%20post%20IRL%2C%20this%20rule%20doesn't%20apply%20if%20you're%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20person%20whose%20exclusion%20from%20the%20chat%20is%20the%20very%20meta%20reason%20for%20the%20chat's%20existence%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20In%20which%20case%2C%20you%20should%20only%20talk%20about%20the%20chat%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20And%20be%20sure%20to%20mention%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20it's%20from%20our%20group%20chat.%20You%20wouldn't%20get%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Your%20level%20of%20activity%20in%20a%20group%20is%20inversely%20proportional%20to%20your%20susceptibility%20to%20a%20side%20chat%20that%20doesn't%20include%20you.%20But%20the%20same%20is%20true%20if%20you're%20%3Cem%3Etoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20active.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20if%20you%20only%20lurk%20and%20never%20chime%20in%20or%20if%20you%20dominate%20the%20conversation%20at%20all%20hours%2C%20you%20only%20have%20yourself%20to%20blame%20if%20you're%20not%20part%20of%20a%20breakout%20chat.%20Grow%20up%2C%20Peter%20Pan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Additions%20to%20the%20group%20chat%20must%20be%20approved%20unanimously.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20must%20ask%20someone%20before%20adding%20them%20to%20an%20existing%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Remember%20the%20Sabbath%2C%20and%20keep%20it%20holy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lines%20between%20work%20and%20life%20are%20blurred%20enough%20on%20Slack%2C%20email%2C%20and%20every%20other%20app.%20Spare%20the%20group%20chat%20work%20talk%20on%20the%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Never%20tweet.%20Share%20it%20in%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20get%20more%20engagement%2C%20you'll%20keep%20the%20blast%20zone%20of%20your%20embarrassment%20contained%2C%20and%20you'll%20keep%20your%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Always%20make%20fun%20of%20the%20person%20with%20the%20green%20bubble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndroid%20users%2C%20you%20signed%20up%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20The%20group%20should%20get%20along%20IRL.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20or%20less.%20We%20all%20know%20how%20old%20friends%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Speaking%20of%2C%20two%20friends%20in%20an%20argument%20with%20each%20other%20in%20a%20chat%20have%20a%20maximum%20of%20four%20insults%20each%20to%20lob%20at%20one%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20you're%20ruining%20the%20vibe.%20Take%20it%20to%20one-on-one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%20Limit%20yourself%20to%20sharing%20no%20more%20than%20four%20memes%2C%20reels%2C%20or%20gifs%20consecutively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnything%20more%20and%20you%20can't%20expect%20anyone%20to%20watch%20them%20all%2C%20and%20you%20sound%20like%20a%20bot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E12.%20Maslow's%20hierarchy%20of%20needs%20applies%20to%20reactions%20in%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20pyramid%20of%20satisfying%20reactions%2C%20a%20response%20that%20acknowledges%20and%20empathizes%20with%20the%20text%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20expands%20on%20the%20conversation%20with%20a%20follow-up%20question%20or%20related%20anecdote%20is%20self-actualized%2C%20which%20is%20better%20than%20a%20joke%20reaction%20(esteem%20need)%20is%20better%20than%20an%20emoji%20reaction%20(love%20and%20belonging%20need)%20is%20better%20than%20reading%20it%20and%20not%20reacting%20at%20all%20(safety%20and%20security%20need)%20is%20better%20than%20an%20iMessage%20reaction%20(physiological%20need).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E13.%20Never%20respond%20with%20%26quot%3Bha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20passive-aggressive%20texts%20a%20person%20can%20send.%20If%20you're%20thinking%20of%20texting%20%26quot%3Bha%2C%26quot%3B%20add%20at%20least%20one%20%26quot%3Bha%26quot%3B%20to%20it%2C%20even%20if%20your%20heart's%20not%20in%20it%2C%20and%20take%20a%20walk.%C2%A0Conversely%2C%20anything%20beyond%20four%20%26quot%3Bha's%26quot%3B%20makes%20it%20sound%20like%20you're%20laughing%20at%20them%20ironically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E14.%20Even%20if%20every%20single%20member%20of%20the%20group%20is%20in%20one%20place%2C%20such%20as%20a%20wedding%2C%20you%20are%20still%20expected%20to%20communicate%20primarily%20via%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%20Because%20this%20is%20how%20we%20communicate%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E15.%20Have%20at%20least%20one%20group%20chat%20that%20serves%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20your%20consciousness%2C%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20your%20and%20your%20friend's%20superego%2C%20ego%2C%20and%20especially%20your%20id.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reporter%20Astead%20Herndon%20once%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20key%20to%20every%20group%20chat%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAsteadWH%2Fstatus%2F1362746415068413959%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emutually%20assured%20destruction%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E16.%20Respond%20to%20what%20you%20want%20to%2C%20when%20you%20want%20to.%20But%20there's%20a%2048-hour%20grace%20period%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20you're%20the%20rare%20person%20in%20the%20chat%20who%20never%20responds%20but%20kills%20when%20you%20do.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20you%20may%20fire%20when%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E17.%20Never%2C%20ever%2C%20ever%20join%20a%20crypto%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Venutolo-Mantovani%20has%20written%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20National%20Geographic%2C%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%20Traveler%2C%20Wired%2C%20and%20many%20others.%20He%20lives%20in%20Chapel%20Hill%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20their%20two%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmodern-etiquette-guide-for-group-chats-better-social-media-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699525801