%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusic%20festivals%20are%20powerful.%20When%20they%20go%20well%2C%20they%20are%20glorious%3B%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20nightmare.%20Ask%20anyone%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20right%20now.%20Because%20music%20festivals%20rely%20on%20the%20superiority%20of%20live%20performance%20as%20an%20aural%20good%20%E2%80%93%20as%20opposed%20to%20recorded%20music%20that%20can%20be%20consumed%20repeatedly%2C%20uniformly%20and%20in%20a%20location-agnostic%20manner%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20meant%20for%20a%20different%2C%20smaller%2C%20kind%20of%20audience.%20And%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20festival%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjodhpurriff.org%2F%5C%22%3EJodhpur-RIFF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20audience%20base%20becomes%20even%20smaller.%20Unlike%20any%20other%20music%20festival%20in%20India%2C%20this%20folk%20and%20roots%20music%20festival%20%E2%80%93%20now%20in%20its%2016th%20year%20%E2%80%93%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20expanding%20that%20base.%20It%20also%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20spelling%20out%20its%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20define%20the%20specific%20nature%20of%20politics.%20For%20some%20politics%20of%20identity%20is%20all%20important%2C%20for%20some%20others%20it%20means%20nothing.%20Even%20if%20I%20stand%20and%20announce%20during%20the%20festival%20that%20we%20are%20Left-leaning%20or%20Right-leaning%2C%20what%20does%20it%20matter%3F%C2%A0%3Ci%3EKalakaar%20ki%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Elife%3Ci%3E%C2%A0par%20kya%20farq%20padta%20hai%3C%2Fi%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20Divya%20Bhatia%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatia%20likes%20to%20see%20Jodhpur-R%3Cspan%3EIFF%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eplaying%20a%20key%20role%20in%20bringing%20artists%2Fsuppliers%20to%20the%20audiences%2Fconsumers%20of%20aural%20goods%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20socio-economist%20P.M.%20Hirsch%E2%80%99s%20vocabulary%20to%20define%20the%20cultural%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20be%20regular%20and%20consistent%20in%20order%20for%20your%20politics%20to%20shine%20through.%20Merely%20speaking%20about%20something%20means%20nothing.%20My%20politics%20is%20about%20facilitating%20artists%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20themselves.%20To%20command%20respect.%20To%20ask%20for%20their%20due%20in%20monetary%20terms.%20The%20mandate%20of%20the%20festival%20has%20been%20to%20give%20a%20platform%20to%20artists%20that%20can%20bring%20a%20change%20to%20their%20personal%20and%20professional%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20sixteen%20years%2C%20Jodhpur-RIFF%20has%20been%20able%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20a%20niche%20festival%20that%20draws%20repeat%20audiences.%20The%20recently%20concluded%202023%20edition%20saw%20some%20people%20who%20have%20never%20missed%20a%20single%20year.%20For%20four%20days%20and%20nights%20music%20lovers%20from%20across%20the%20world%20congregate%20in%20the%20medieval%20fort%20of%20Mehrangarh%20absorbing%20the%20sights%20and%20sounds%20of%20the%20collaborative%20congress%20of%20performance%20artists.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20not-for-profit%20festival%20so%20the%20scale%20has%20to%20be%20kept%20optimal.%20We%20do%20not%20spend%20anything%20on%20marketing%20and%20publicity%20so%20that%20we%20can%20pay%20the%20artists.%20People%20come%20to%20the%20festival%20year%20after%20year%20because%20they%20get%20something%20here%20which%20is%20matchless%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhatia%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20music%20festivals%20are%20not%20a%20new%20phenomenon.%20Remember%2C%20French%20composer%20Claude%20Debussy%20heard%20Javanese%20gamelan%20music%20at%20the%201889%20World%20Exhibition%20in%20Paris.%20Expressing%20traditional%20diversity%20of%20different%20cultures%2C%20Jodhpur-RIFF%20is%20an%20ideal%20space%20for%20multicultural%20encounters%20where%20the%20festival%20goer%20comes%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Own%E2%80%99.%20This%20year%E2%80%99s%20festival%20hosted%20musicians%20from%20across%20the%20world%20who%20brought%20their%20unique%20musical%20traditions%20and%20also%20collaborated%20on%20the%20spot%20with%20each%20other%20in%20a%20celebration%20of%20plurality.%20The%20festival%20customarily%20features%20a%20grand%20jam%20called%20%E2%80%98RIFF-Rustle%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20grand%20finale%20when%20artists%20respond%20to%20each%20other%20in%20a%20carnivalesque%20manner.%20The%20Bakhtinian%20idea%20of%20different%20voices%20interacting%20in%20order%20to%20create%20meaning%20in%20a%20particular%20context%20can%20be%20experienced%20live%20during%20this%20improvisation.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20being%20pedagogical%20where%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20need%20to%20do%20so.%20Sometimes%2C%20joy%20ought%20to%20take%20over%20intellect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoy%20can%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20little%20schoolgirl%20who%20wants%20to%20become%20%E2%80%9Ca%20great%20artist%20like%20my%20mother%E2%80%9D.%20And%20why%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20you%20if%20your%20mother%20is%20Asha%20Sapera%2C%20a%20renowned%20dancer%20from%20the%20snake-charmer%20tribe%20of%20Rajasthan%3F%20Traditional%20arts%20can%20only%20flourish%20through%20intergenerational%20carrying%20forward.%20But%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20choice%20and%20not%20compulsion%20or%20helplessness.%20The%20words%20of%20Asha%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Nandini%2C%20fluently%20enunciated%20in%20English%2C%20perhaps%20herald%20a%20welcome%20era%20of%20choice.%20And%20maybe%20this%20is%20what%20Bhatia%20means%20when%20he%20says%20that%20artistes%20ought%20to%20learn%20how%20the%20market%20forces%20operate%20and%20make%20them%20work%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20artistic%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09140635%2Fimage-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09140635%2Fimage-1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09140635%2Fimage-1-300x225.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09140635%2Fimage-1-1024x768.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684271%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAsha%20Sapera%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20Nandini.%20Photo%3A%20Nishtha%20Gautam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArtistes%20also%20operate%20within%20hierarchies%20and%20they%20have%20internal%20pulls%20and%20pushes.%20Like%2C%20each%20year%20I%20get%20requests%20from%20musicians%20wanting%20to%20play%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98main%20stage%E2%80%99%20venue%20of%20the%20festival.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20is%20that%20they%20have%20figured%20out%20that%20%E2%80%98main%20stage%E2%80%99%20performers%20get%20paid%20more.%20This%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%20Folk%20artistes%20are%20also%20getting%20more%20aware%20of%20parity%20with%20commercial%20musicians%20playing%20in%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArt%20survives%20amidst%20death%20and%20destruction.%20Bertolt%20Brecht%E2%80%99s%20famous%20line%20on%20singing%20about%20dark%20days%20underscores%20its%20resilience.%20It%20cannot%2C%20however%2C%20exist%20in%20a%20vacuum%20of%20political%20economy.%20In%20simple%20words%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20for%20art%20to%20exist%20without%20a%20market%C2%A0but%20the%3Cspan%3En%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20artiste%20cannot%20survive.%20An%20empowered%20artiste%C2%A0is%20the%C2%A0one%20who%20makes%20the%20market%20work%20for%20their%20artistic%20production%20and%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20Art%20transforms%20into%20a%20pastiche%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20tools%20to%20negotiate%20the%20cultural%20materialism%20of%20its%20age.%20And%20this%20is%20where%20festivals%20like%20Jodhpur-RIFF%20have%20a%20key%20role%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAspirations%20and%20altruism%20need%20to%20be%20aligned%20in%20a%20way%20that%20art%20remains%20the%20refuge%20of%20the%20gifted%2C%20not%20the%20scoundrel.%20The%20pursuit%20of%20art%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20a%20torment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20existential%20torment%20of%20the%20artiste%2C%20it%20engenders%20joy.%20For%20the%20artistes%20as%20well%20as%20their%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20Leonard%20Cohen%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CO%20beloved%20speaking%2C%20O%20comfort%20whispering%20in%20the%20terror%2C%20unspeakable%20explanation%20of%20the%20smoke%20and%20cruelty%2C%20undo%20the%20self-conspiracy%2C%20let%20me%20dare%20the%20boldness%20of%20joy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fnishtha-gautam-1%5C%22%3ENishtha%20Gautam%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20author%2C%20academic%2C%20and%20columnist.%20She%E2%80%99s%20the%20co-editor%20of%20a%20critically%20acclaimed%20volume%20on%20strategic%20affairs%20titled%20%3C%2Fem%3EIn%20Hard%20Times%3A%20Security%20in%20Times%20of%20Insecurity%3Cem%3E%20(Bloomsbury%2C%202022).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699524023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09140959%2FFew5f1NaMAE4Mwg.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fjodhpur-riff-music-festival-multicultural-encounters%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20niche%20festival%20has%20been%20able%20to%20draw%20repeat%20audiences.%20The%20recently%20concluded%202023%20edition%20saw%20some%20people%20who%20have%20never%20missed%20a%20single%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fjodhpur-riff-music-festival-multicultural-encounters%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22