p%3ETheir%20letter%20came%20a%20month%20after%20Hamas%20attacked%20communities%20in%20southern%20Israel%2C%20killing%20over%201%2C400%20people%2C%20injuring%20about%205%2C400%20others%20and%20taking%20around%20240%20hostage%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2023%2F11%2F08%2Fisrael-gaza-war-protest-congress-palestine-students-raytheon%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Israeli%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20retaliated%20with%20a%20brutal%20offensive%20into%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20home%20territory%2C%20Gaza%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20at%20least%2010%2C569%20people%20and%20around%2026%2C475%20others%20being%20wounded%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20health%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20of%2036%20Brown%20University%20students%20said%20they%20condemned%20the%20violence%20by%20both%20sides%20and%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20disentangle%20this%20violence%20from%20the%20political%20context%20in%20which%20it%20arose%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20identified%20this%20political%20context%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20decades-long%20history%20of%20state-sanctioned%20and%20expansionist%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20said%20Israel%20had%20pursued%20%E2%80%9C75%20years%20of%20apartheid%20and%20occupation%E2%80%9D%20prior%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20cannot%20acknowledge%20and%20reject%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20indiscriminate%20killing%20of%20thousands%20and%20forced%20displacement%20of%20over%201.5%20million%20Palestinians%2C%20then%20we%20have%20failed%20to%20learn%20from%20our%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20students%20also%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20historic%20persecution%20faced%20by%20the%20Jewish%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20their%20call%20for%20freedom%20for%20Palestinians%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20forced%20removal%20of%20Jews%20from%20Palestinian%20land%2C%20the%20students%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C