uot%3Bis%20no%20longer%20sustainable%2C%20financially%20nor%20psychologically%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fomegle-videotelephony-omegle-shutting-down-5-points-on-online-chat-website-4560179%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fomegle-videotelephony-omegle-shutting-down-5-points-on-online-chat-website-4560179%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fomegle-videotelephony-omegle-shutting-down-5-points-on-online-chat-website-4560179%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20The%20Scientists%20Revealed%20At%20Mexican%20Congress%20During%20Second%20UFO%20Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20Mexico%20Congress%20stunned%20the%20world%20with%20their%20display%20of%20two%20alleged%20Peruvian%20'alien%20corpses'%2C%20a%20second%20Congressional%20hearing%20was%20held%20on%20Tuesday.%20Researchers%20testified%20before%20Mexico's%20Congress%20and%20declared%20that%20the%20previously%20displayed%20three-fingered%20Peruvian%20mummies%20were%20authentic.%20However%2C%20they%20did%20not%20confirm%20that%20the%20remains%20were%20aliens%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EReuters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20''non-human''%20alien%20corpses%2C%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%201%2C000-year-old%20fossilised%20remains%20of%20extraterrestrial%20individuals%2C%20were%C2%A0presented%20in%20windowed%20boxes%2C%20by%20journalist%20and%20ufologist%20Jaime%20Maussan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Findings%20about%20the%20Peruvian%20Mummies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Mr.%20Maussan%20returned%20to%20Congress%20to%20emphasise%20the%20genuine%20nature%20of%20the%20bodies.%20During%20the%20session%2C%C2%A0Mr.%20Maussan%20was%20backed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20medical%20experts%20who%20said%20that%20the%20mummies%20were%20once-living%20organisms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20alien%20enthusiast%20and%20his%20group%20of%20researchers%20showed%20photographs%20and%20X-rays%20of%20what%20he%20said%20was%20a%20''non-human%20being.''%20Mr%20Maussan%20said%20the%20bodies%20belonged%20to%20a%20''new%20species%2C''%20as%20they%20lacked%20lungs%20and%20ribs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnthropologist%20Roger%20Zuniga%20of%20San%20Luis%20Gonzaga%20National%20University%20in%20Ica%2C%20Peru%2C%20supported%20the%20findings%2C%20and%20said%20%26quot%3BThey're%20real%26quot%3B.%20''There%20was%20absolutely%20no%20human%20intervention%20in%20the%20physical%20and%20biological%20formation%20of%20these%20beings%2C''%20he%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMr%20Zuniga%20presented%20a%20letter%20signed%20by%2011%20researchers%20from%20the%20university%20declaring%20the%20same.%20The%20letter%20made%20clear%2C%20however%2C%20they%20were%20not%20implying%20the%20bodies%20were%20%26quot%3Bextraterrestrial%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congressman%20Sergio%20Gutierrez%2C%20from%20President%20Andres%20Manuel%20Lopez%20Obrador's%20ruling%20Morena%20party%2C%20called%20for%20a%20reform%20to%20Mexico's%20law%20to%20make%20all%20information%20about%20UFOs%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20happened%20during%20the%20first%20UFO%20session%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20tiny%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwatch-mysterious-non-human-alien-corpses-displayed-at-mexicos-congress-4386001%5C%22%3Emummified%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0were%20presented%20to%20Mexico's%20Congress%20on%20September%2013%2C%20images%20of%20which%20were%20beamed%20around%20the%20world%2C%20sparking%20excitement%20and%20curiosity.%20The%20mysterious%20bodies%20were%20tiny%20in%20stature%20and%20chalky%20in%20colour%2C%20and%20each%20one%20of%20them%20had%20three-fingered%20hands%20and%20shrunken%20heads.%C2%A0One%20was%20described%20as%20female%2C%20with%20eggs%20inside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Maussan%20claimed%20they%20were%20found%20around%202017%20in%20Peru%2C%20near%20the%20pre-Columbian%20Nazca%20Lines.%20He%20added%20that%20they%20were%20about%201%2C000%20years%20old%2C%20and%20analyzed%20through%20a%20carbon%20dating%20process%20by%20Mexico's%20National%20Autonomous%20University%20(UNAM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%C2%A0Mexican%20doctors%20conducted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flab-tests-carried-out-on-mexicos-alien-bodies-no-evidence-of-any-assembly-4405402%5C%22%3Eextensive%20laboratory%20studies%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20two%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%26quot%3B%20alien%20corpses%20and%20found%20%26quot%3Bno%20evidence%20of%20any%20assembly%20or%20manipulation%20of%20the%20skulls%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%20doctors%20said%20that%20the%20so-called%20bodies%20belonged%20to%20a%20single%20skeleton.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20UFO%20and%20forensics%20experts%20slammed%20the%20claims%20as%20''unsubstantiated''%20and%20a%20''hoax''.%20Some%20academics%20and%20archaeologists%20suggested%20the%20%26quot%3Bbodies%26quot%3B%20are%20simply%20the%20ancient%20remains%20of%20mummified%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699519800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fglre1ak8_peruvian-mummies_625x300_09_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fperuvian-mummies-aliens-new-species-what-the-scientists-revealed-at-mexican-congress-during-second-ufo-session-4560064%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20second%20Congress%20session%2C%20Mr.%20Maussan%20was%20backed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20medical%20experts%20who%20said%20that%20the%20mummies%20were%20once-living%20organisms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fperuvian-mummies-aliens-new-species-what-the-scientists-revealed-at-mexican-congress-during-second-ufo-session-4560064%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fperuvian-mummies-aliens-new-species-what-the-scientists-revealed-at-mexican-congress-during-second-ufo-session-4560064%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fperuvian-mummies-aliens-new-species-what-the-scientists-revealed-at-mexican-congress-during-second-ufo-session-4560064%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Watershed%20Moment%20in%20German%20History%20That%20Created%20Adolf%20Hitler%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F16095947%2FHitler_salute_in_front_of_lamppost.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShortly%20before%20midnight%20on%20May%2031%2C%201962%2C%20Adolf%20Eichmann%20was%20hanged%20inside%20the%20maximum%20security%20Ramla%20prison%2C%20south%20of%20Tel%20Aviv.%20Earlier%20that%20evening%2C%20president%20Yitzhak%20Ben-Zvi%20had%20turned%20down%20Eichmann%E2%80%99s%20mercy%20plea%20post%20his%20conviction%20and%20sentencing%20by%20a%20Jerusalem%20court%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENazis%20%26amp%3B%20Nazi%20Collaborators%20Punishment%20Act%2C%201950%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2056-year-old%20Nazi%20had%20been%20found%20guilty%20of%20war%20crimes%2C%20crimes%20against%20the%20Jewish%20people%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20later%20confirmed%20the%20conviction%20and%20the%20sentence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20crematorium%20had%20been%20specially%20built%20on%20the%20prison%20compound%20because%20Eichmann%20had%20requested%20to%20be%20cremated%2C%20though%20traditional%20Jewish%20custom%20forbade%20cremation.%20Early%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20June%201%2C%201962%2C%20before%20sunrise%2C%20the%20ashes%20were%20taken%20out%20on%20a%20police%20motorboat%20and%20scattered%20in%20the%20sea%20six%20miles%20beyond%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20waters%3B%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20shores%20could%20scarcely%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20soiled%20by%20Nazi%20detritus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09124955%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09124955%2Funnamed.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09124955%2Funnamed-300x252.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684243%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdolf%20Eichmann%20(inside%20his%20bullet-proof%20glass%20booth)%20at%20his%20trial%2C%201961.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20two%20men%20charged%20with%20the%20disposal%20of%20Eichmann%E2%80%99s%20ashes%20was%20Meilach%20Goldman-Gilead%2C%20an%20Auschwitz%20survivor%20aged%2037.%20Goldman%20was%20a%20Polish%20Jew%20who%20had%20moved%20to%20Israel%20in%20the%20early%201950s%20and%20was%20now%20a%20police%20officer%20requisitioned%20to%20help%20in%20the%20Eichmann%20trial%20as%20one%20of%20the%20junior%20prosecutors.%20The%20ashes%20had%20been%20placed%20in%20a%20two-litre%20milk%20jar%20no%20more%20than%20three-quarters%20full%2C%20and%20Goldman%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20little%20ash%20remained%20of%20a%20human%20adult.%20It%20was%20at%20that%20point%20that%20Goldman%20had%20his%20epiphany%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CStanding%20there%2C%20I%20remembered%20that%20about%20a%20week%20after%20I%20had%20arrived%20at%20Birkenau%2C%20in%20November%2C%201943%2C%20I%20was%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20block%20with%20a%20group%20of%20some%20ten%20prisoners%2C%20and%20we%20were%20led%20towards%20the%20crematoria.%20We%20already%20knew%20what%20was%20happening%20there%2C%20and%20thought%20we%20were%20being%20led%20to%20our%20death.%20The%20ground%20was%20icy%20and%20we%20were%20walking%20with%20our%20wooden%20%E2%80%98Dutch%E2%80%99%20shoes.%20A%20Polish%20%E2%80%98capo%E2%80%99%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20prisoner%20coopted%20as%20a%20forced%20labour%20supervisor%20or%20prison%20guard)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estood%20there%2C%20with%20some%20SS%20men.%20We%20were%20brought%20to%20a%20mountain%20of%20ash.%20We%20were%20told%20to%20get%20wheelbarrows%2C%20fill%20them%20with%20ash%2C%20and%20scatter%20it%20on%20the%20routes%20the%20SS%20guards%20would%20take%20during%20their%20patrols%2C%20so%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20slip.%20It%20was%20a%20full%20day%E2%80%99s%20job.%20Later%20we%20were%20returned%20to%20the%20camp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6Immediately%20after%20they%20had%20removed%20Eichmann%E2%80%99s%20body%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efrom%20the%20oven)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20I%20saw%20what%20little%20was%20left%20of%20it%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20many%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20must%20have%20been%20in%20that%20ash%20pile%20at%20Birkenau.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20association%20I%20will%20not%20forget%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20way%20Gilead%20could%20have%20forgotten.%20A%20gangly%2017-year-old%20in%201942%2C%20he%20had%20looked%20on%20helplessly%20as%20his%20parents%20and%2010-year-old%20sister%20were%20bundled%20off%20to%20the%20Belzec%20death%20camp%2C%20where%20all%20three%20were%20to%20be%20gassed%20to%20death.%20Adolf%20Eichmann%20had%20been%20the%20%E2%80%98Final%20Solution%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20top%20gun%2C%20overseeing%20with%20clinical%20efficiency%20the%20deportation%20of%20European%20Jews%20to%20the%20rash%20of%20extermination%20camps%20that%20occupied%20Poland%20was%20dotted%20with.%20It%20was%20unsurprising%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20the%20first%20time%20Goldman%20sat%20opposite%20Eichmann%20to%20take%20down%20his%20testimony%20before%20the%20trial%20and%20Eichmann%20opened%20his%20mouth%20to%20speak%2C%20Goldman%20%E2%80%9Chad%20the%20feeling%20I%20was%20seeing%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20crematorium%20open%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20disposed%20of%20Eichmann%E2%80%99s%20ashes%2C%20Goldman%20and%20his%20colleague%20described%20their%20journey%20back%20like%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%20%5Bwe%20were%5D%20headed%20back%2C%20and%20the%20Sun%20had%20come%20up.%20The%20fishermen%20were%20returning%20from%20their%20nighttime%20fishing%2C%20and%20we%20saw%20Tel%20Aviv%20awaken%20to%20a%20new%20day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6..%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20suddenly%20felt%20we%20were%20alive%3A%20the%20Sun%20was%20shining%E2%80%A6.%5Band%5D%20the%20nightmare%20was%20over.%20A%20new%20chapter%20had%20begun.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20422px)%2085vw%2C%20422px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125124%2Funnamed-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22422%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125124%2Funnamed-1.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125124%2Funnamed-1-300x210.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684244%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22295%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHolocaust%20survivor%20Abba%20Kovner%20testifying%20at%20Eichmann%E2%80%99s%20trial.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Eichmann%E2%80%99s%20trial%20and%20execution%2C%20Nazism%20could%20plausibly%20be%20thought%20to%20have%20run%20its%20course.%20The%20naivete%20of%20such%20optimism%2C%20though%2C%20was%20to%20become%20apparent%20fairly%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20To%20Israel%2C%20at%20any%20rate%2C%20it%20looked%20as%20though%20Nazism%20had%20been%20exorcised%20for%20good%3A%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20it%20extraordinary%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Jewish%20state%20which%20happened%20to%20send%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20executioner-in-chief%20to%20the%20gallows%3F%20Monsters%20such%20as%20Josef%20Mengele%20and%20Klaus%20Barbie%20still%20remained%20at%20large%20%E2%80%93%20but%20for%20then%20it%20seemed%20not%20far-fetched%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20nightmare%20was%20finally%20over.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20if%20the%20Eichmann%20trial%20marked%20the%20end%20of%20Nazism%20in%20a%20manner%20of%20speaking%2C%20was%20there%20a%20point%20in%20time%20that%20could%20conceivably%20be%20described%20as%20Nazism%E2%80%99s%20jumping-off%20point%2C%20its%20opening%20gambit%3F%20Can%20we%20identify%20a%20watershed%2C%20a%20moment%20which%20set%20Nazism%20on%20course%20for%20its%20murderous%20later%20ascendancy%2C%20even%20though%20that%20ascendancy%20could%20not%20necessarily%20have%20been%20visualised%20at%20that%20point%3F%20I%20will%20argue%20there%20indeed%20was%20such%20a%20point%2C%20a%20crossroads%20from%20where%20several%20distinct%20pathways%20radiated%20out%2C%20some%20likelier%20to%20be%20followed%20than%20the%20rest%2C%20but%20as%20has%20often%20happened%20in%20history%2C%20the%20choice%20made%20was%20as%20fortuitous%20as%20it%20was%20bizarre.%20But%20being%20fortuitous%20did%20not%20stop%20it%20from%20leading%20up%20to%20one%20of%20the%20goriest%20episodes%20of%20blood-letting%20in%20recorded%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20tipping%20point%20was%20a%20set%20of%20extraordinary%20events%20that%20played%20out%20in%20Munich%20exactly%20one%20100%20years%20ago%20today%2C%20on%20November%209%2C%201923.%20Elsewhere%20I%20have%20referred%20to%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20proceedings%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbeer-hall-putsch-november-9-1923-germanys-9-11%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Germany%E2%80%99s%20own%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbeer-hall-putsch-november-9-1923-germanys-9-11%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E9%2F11%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20but%20probably%20that%20description%20somewhat%20downplays%20the%20momentousness%20of%20their%20repercussions.%20The%20terrifying%20attacks%20of%20September%2011%2C%202001%20on%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20Twin%20Towers%20were%20no%20doubt%20a%20particularly%20ghastly%20terrorist%20strike%20with%20a%20vast%20number%20of%20victims.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sequel%20to%20the%20attacks%20was%20even%20deadlier%2C%20because%20by%20announcing%20that%209%2F11%20had%20changed%20everything%20%E2%80%93%20the%20US%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edid%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Echange%20everything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Foperation-valkyrie-failed-plot-adolf-hitler%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Operation%20Valkyrie%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Failed%20Plot%20to%20Kill%20Adolf%20Hitler%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20US%20President%20George%20W.%20Bush%20declared%20war%20on%20Saddam%20Hussain%20(who%20was%20not%20an%20actor%20in%20the%209%2F11%20drama)%2C%20much%20of%20West%20Asia%20was%20plunged%20in%20the%20most%20violent%20chaos%2C%20perhaps%20for%20all%20of%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20vast%20swathes%20of%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20were%20laid%20waste%2C%20the%20ISIS%20was%20born%20and%20thrived%2C%20millions%20of%20ordinary%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20were%20killed%20and%20some%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20notably%20Syria%20and%20Yemen%E2%80%93%20were%20also%20mutilated%20beyond%20recognition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20gainsaying%20all%20of%20that%20%E2%80%93%20but%20what%20happened%20on%20that%20fateful%20November%20morning%20in%20Munich%20belongs%20in%20an%20altogether%20different%20league.%20For%2C%20if%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20found%20itself%20staring%20at%20the%20apocalypse%2C%20it%20was%20thanks%20to%20the%20extraordinary%20train%20of%20events%20set%20in%20motion%20that%20day.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20bloodiest%20war%20%E2%80%93%20consuming%20no%20fewer%20than%2080%20million%20lives%3B%20the%20unspeakable%20bestiality%20of%20the%20Holocaust%3B%20the%20forced%20migration%2C%20in%20Europe%20alone%2C%20of%2075%2B%20million%20humans%3B%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20atomic%20bomb%20blasts%20over%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki.%20These%20and%20other%20spectacular%20abominations%20make%20up%20the%20grisly%20harvest%20of%20what%20November%209%2C%202023%20sowed%20on%20German%20soil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125347%2Funnamed-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125347%2Funnamed-2.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125347%2Funnamed-2-300x216.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMunich%20city%20council%20members%20being%20taken%20hostage%20by%20the%20puschists.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20what%20happened%3F%20In%20the%20early%20afternoon%20that%20day%2C%20Hitler%20led%20about%202%2C000%20of%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKampfbund%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eacolytes%2C%20all%20variously%20armed%2C%20on%20a%20violent%20and%20raucous%20march%20to%20Munich%E2%80%99s%20city%20centre.%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20original%20project%20had%20been%20more%20grandiose%3A%20a%20march%20on%20Berlin%20to%20seize%20political%20power%20by%20throwing%20out%20the%20%E2%80%98vile%2C%20Jewry-infested%E2%80%99%20Weimar%20Republic.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20hoping%20to%20mimic%20Benito%20Mussolini%E2%80%99s%20triumphant%20march%20on%20Rome%20of%20one%20year%20prior%2C%20the%20march%20that%20catapulted%20the%20Fascist%20supremo%20to%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Italian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIl%20Duce.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20wildly%20fanciful%20plan%20had%20fallen%20through%20when%20he%20failed%20to%20get%20Bavaria%E2%80%99s%20far-right%20state%20commissioner%20and%20its%20military%20and%20police%20chiefs%20%E2%80%93%20who%20had%20at%20some%20point%20been%20co-conspirators%20%E2%80%93%20on%20board%20his%20plot.%20The%20night%20before%20had%20been%20tumultuous.%20In%20a%20scene%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20knockabout%20farce%2C%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20men%20waylaid%20a%20large%20political%20rally%20ongoing%20in%20Munich%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBurgerbraukeller%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ebeer-hall%2C%20shooed%20the%20speakers%20off%20the%20stage%20and%20held%20them%20hostage%2C%20leaving%20the%20floor%20open%20for%20Hitler%20to%20make%20a%20dramatic%20entry.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20fired%20pistol%20shots%20in%20the%20air%20and%20proceeded%20to%20harangue%20the%203000-strong%20gathering%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98illegitimacy%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Berlin%20government%2C%20announce%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Weimar%20Republic%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98national%20socialist%20revolution%E2%80%99.%20Later%20that%20night%2C%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20men%20occupied%20the%20war%20ministry%20complex%2C%20raided%20arms%20caches%2C%20plundered%20currency-printing%20presses%2C%20vandalised%20Jewish%20businesses%20and%20a%20prominent%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20office%20and%20kidnapped%20Munich%E2%80%99s%20mayor%20and%20his%20council%20members.%20But%20as%20dawn%20broke%20on%20November%209%2C%20support%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98revolution%E2%80%99%20evaporated%20and%20the%20regular%20army%20and%20the%20police%20came%20out%20in%20strength%20to%20put%20it%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20loss%20what%20to%20do%20and%20increasingly%20listless%2C%20Hitler%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20little%20man%20in%20an%20old%20waterproof%20coat%20with%20a%20revolver%20at%20his%20hip%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20York%20Times%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EMunich%20correspondent%20wrote%20in%20his%20despatch%2C%20%E2%80%9Cscarcely%20seemed%20to%20fill%20the%20part%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20strapping%20young%20leader%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoup%20d%E2%80%99etat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fhow-fear-of-communism-led-to-the-rise-of-hitler-and-nazism%5C%22%3EHow%20Fear%20of%20Communism%20Led%20to%20the%20Rise%20of%20Hitler%2C%20Nazism%20and%20World%20War%20Two%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20army%20had%20meanwhile%20driven%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20men%20out%20of%20the%20war%20ministry.%20Something%20had%20to%20be%20done%20quickly%2C%20and%20when%20someone%20suggested%20a%20march%20on%20the%20city%20centre%2C%20Hitler%2C%20aware%20that%20it%20was%20a%20desperate%2C%20possibly%20fatal%2C%20gamble%2C%20agreed.%20The%20marchers%20set%20off%20on%20their%20outrageous%20last-gasp%20mission.%20Inevitably%2C%20there%20ensued%20a%20deadly%20showdown%20with%20law%20enforcement%20near%20Odeonplatz.%20In%20the%20mayhem%20that%20followed%2C%20four%20Bavarian%20policemen%20and%20fifteen%20Nazi%20marchers%20%E2%80%93%20besides%20an%20ill-fated%20bystander%20%E2%80%93%20were%20shot%20to%20death.%20Hitler%20fled%20the%20scene%20(with%20only%20a%20dislocated%20shoulder)%2C%20leaving%20his%20dead%20and%20dying%20comrades%20to%20their%20own%20devices%2C%20and%20hid%20for%20two%20days%20inside%20the%20loft%20of%20a%20friend%E2%80%99s%20house%20at%20some%20distance%20from%20Munich.%20His%20injured%20arm%20in%20a%20sling%2C%20the%20future%20arbiter%20of%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20destiny%20was%20disconsolate%20with%20despair%20and%20considered%20suicide.%20On%20November%2011%2C%201923%2C%20the%20police%20arrived%20to%20pick%20him%20up.%20Dressed%20in%20no%20more%20than%20a%20borrowed%2C%20loose-fitting%20bathrobe%2C%20Hitler%20gave%20himself%20up.%20He%20knew%20that%2C%20at%20a%20minimum%2C%20a%20sizeable%20prison%20sentence%2C%20even%20a%20likely%20deportation%2C%20awaited%20him.%20Hitler%20reckoned%20it%20was%20the%20end%20of%20the%20road%20for%20him%20and%20his%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125459%2Funnamed.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125459%2Funnamed.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125459%2Funnamed-300x133.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125459%2Funnamed-1024x453.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684248%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22531%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHitler%20and%20the%20other%20leaders%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98revolution%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20not%20alone%20in%20thinking%20thus.%20The%20world%20outside%20more%20than%20agreed%20with%20him.%20On%20November%2010%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Manchester%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20how%20%E2%80%9C(t)he%20German%20reactionaries%20have%20struck%20and%20failed%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Edid%20not%20disagree.%20%E2%80%98Reichswehr%20Troops%20Crush%20Bavarian%20Revolt%E2%80%99%2C%20ran%20the%20most%20prominent%20headline%20of%20the%20newspaper%E2%80%99s%20front%20page.%20In%20an%20opinion%20piece%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENYT%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommented%3A%E2%80%99The%20Burgerbrau%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoup%20d%E2%80%99etat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20the%20craziest%20farce%20pulled%20off%20in%20memory%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20German%20and%20continental%20press%20was%20often%20more%20dismissive%2C%20rubbishing%20the%20uprising%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Beer%20Hall%20Putsch%E2%80%99.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBerliner%20Tagleblatt%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20it%20a%20childish%20prank.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELe%20Petit%20Parisien%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Edubbed%20the%20performance%20sheer%20vaudeville.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELe%20Matin%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ecompared%20it%20to%20a%20carnivalesque%20adventure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVossische%20Zeitung%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eopined%20that%20the%20end%20had%20come%20for%20%E2%80%98charlatan%20Hitler%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFrankfurter%20Zeitung%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eactually%20ran%20an%20obit%20on%20the%20Nazi%20Party.%20In%20his%20defeat%2C%20Hitler%20looked%20ludicrous%20and%20nowhere%20near%20menacing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20of%20history%E2%80%99s%20great%20ironies%2C%20however%2C%20his%20weakest%20moment%20metamorphosed%20swiftly%20into%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20moment%20of%20triumph.%20The%20disgraced%20leader%20of%20a%20thuggish%20band%20of%20no%20more%20than%20a%20few%20thousand%20men%20had%20a%20fairy-tale%20image%20makeover.%20The%20circumstances%20that%20combined%20to%20create%20that%20miracle%20make%20for%20an%20absorbing%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20there%20was%20a%20great%20outpouring%20of%20public%20support%20for%20Hitler%20and%20the%20Nazis%20in%20Bavaria%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20Germany%2C%20where%20antisemitism%20and%20anti-republicanism%20already%20ran%20rife.%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20and%20ensuing%20trial%20were%20noisily%20celebrated%20in%20and%20around%20Munich%20as%20a%20martyr%E2%80%99s%20oblation%20to%20his%20fatherland%2C%20thus%20turning%20a%20little-known%20rabble-rouser%20into%20a%20serious%20political%20actor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20the%20abortive%20march%20and%20the%20trial%20focussed%20on%20Hitler%20such%20public%20attention%20in%20and%20outside%20Germany%20as%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20ever%20have%20dreamed%20of.%20Three%2C%20the%20Bavarian%20authorities%20themselves%20were%20more%20than%20keen%20to%20downplay%20the%20criminality%20of%20the%20Nazi%20misadventure.%20They%20had%20much%20to%20fear%20for%2C%20including%20a%20possible%20unveiling%20of%20the%20close%20links%20that%20top%20men%20of%20the%20state%20administration%20maintained%20with%20Hitler%20till%20just%20before%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoup%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20proximity%20ensured%20that%20Hitler%20and%20the%20others%20were%20arraigned%20only%20for%20%E2%80%98high%20treason%E2%80%99.%20The%20five%20policemen%20killed%2C%20many%20Jewish%20establishments%20vandalised%2C%20government%20officials%20kidnapped%2C%20arms%20and%20cash%20plundered%2C%20a%20prominent%20newspaper%20office%20burnt%20to%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%93%20all%20these%20serious%20charges%20were%20ignored%20in%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20trial%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20not%20merely%20a%20travesty%20of%20justice%20but%20also%20a%20moral%20outrage%3A%20it%20provided%20him%20with%20the%20ideal%20platform%20for%20broadcasting%2C%20virtually%20unchecked%2C%20his%20odious%20views%20on%20nearly%20everything%20on%20earth%2C%20from%20%E2%80%98the%20numberless%20vices%20of%20Jewry%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20%E2%80%98evil%20machinations%20of%20Marxists%20and%20Bolshevists%E2%80%99%20to%20how%20Germany%20had%20been%20stabbed%20in%20the%20back%20by%20%E2%80%98the%20November%20criminals%E2%80%99%20and%20forced%20to%20sign%20a%20dishonourable%20peace%20in%20the%20first%20World%20War.%20In%20his%20long%2C%20shrill%20defence%20arguments%2C%20Hitler%20cynically%20but%20adroitly%20whipped%20up%20antisemitic%20and%20anticommunist%20sentiments%20which%20found%20echoes%20inside%20the%20courthouse%20and%20outside%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125522%2Funnamed-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125522%2Funnamed-3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125522%2Funnamed-3-300x229.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09125522%2Funnamed-3-1024x781.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684249%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22915%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdolf%20Hitler%20serving%20the%20%E2%80%98prison%20sentence%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20choice%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20%E2%80%93%20as%20unusual%20as%20it%20was%20baffling%20%E2%80%93%20contributed%20in%20no%20small%20measure%20to%20the%20trial%E2%80%99s%20eventual%20outcome.%20Logically%2C%20Hitler%20should%20have%20been%20tried%20at%20the%20federal-jurisdiction%20Leipzig%20special%20state%20court%2C%20which%20would%20likely%20have%20handed%20down%20the%20death%20sentence%2C%20or%20at%20any%20rate%20deported%20Hitler%2C%20an%20Austrian%20national%2C%20to%20his%20home%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20rightwing%20Bavarian%20administration%20defied%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20had%20Hitler%20tried%20at%20Munich%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98People%E2%80%99s%20Court%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20featured%20a%20mixed%20bench%20of%20two%20professional%20judges%20and%20three%20lay%20judges%20and%20disallowed%20any%20appeals%20against%20its%20judgements.%20All%20the%20judges%20had%20unabashedly%20far-right%2C%20ultranationalist%20sympathies%20and%20allowed%20Hitler%20full%20play%20of%20his%20demagogical%20skills.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHitler%20insisted%20he%20was%20%E2%80%98out-and-out%20a%20German%20patriot%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20judges%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20more%2C%20thereby%20ruling%20out%20his%20deportation.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20that%20charade%20of%20a%20trial%2C%20the%20judges%20sentenced%20Hitler%20to%20a%20mere%20five-year%20jail%20term.%20Even%20more%20incredibly%2C%20he%20was%20to%20be%20paroled%20after%20only%20eight%20months%20of%20prison-time%20on%20account%20of%20%E2%80%98exemplary%20conduct%E2%80%99!%20On%20December%2020%2C%201924%2C%20Hitler%20walked%20out%20of%20jail%20to%20a%20hero%E2%80%99s%20welcome.%20The%20convicted%20criminal%20had%20transmogrified%20into%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Fuehrer.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20his%20disappointments%20and%20failures%20behind%20him%2C%20he%20would%20now%20march%20relentlessly%20towards%20his%20hideous%20goals.%20The%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%20was%20that%20he%20penned%20his%20convoluted%2C%20obnoxious%20opus%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMein%20Kampf%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20safe%20haven%20of%20his%20comfortable%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFestungshaft%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eprison-house%2C%20one%20of%20the%20mildest%20jail%20sentences%20under%20German%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20perhaps%20not%20idle%20to%20speculate%20what%20might%20have%20happened%20if%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EHitler%20was%20to%20get%20killed%20on%20November%209%2C%201923%20at%20Munich%E2%80%99s%20Odeonplatz.%20(After%20all%2C%20the%20man%20he%20had%20locked%20arms%20with%20as%20they%20marched%2C%20Scheubner-Richter%2C%20had%20been%20shot%20through%20his%20lungs%20and%20died%20instantly.)%20Or%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trial%20that%20magically%20changed%20his%2C%20and%20Nazism%E2%80%99s%2C%20fortunes%20were%20to%20be%20somewhat%20less%20perverse%20than%20it%20actually%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECounterfactuals%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20pass%C3%A9%20in%20historical%20inquiry%2C%20but%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20smother%20the%20thought%20that%2C%20had%20November%209%20not%20played%20out%20as%20insanely%20as%20it%20did%2C%20we%20might%20have%20been%20living%20in%20a%20different%20world%20than%20what%20history%20bequeathed%20to%20us.%20And%20it%20may%20not%20thus%20be%20inapposite%20to%20trace%20Nazism%E2%80%99s%20take-off%20moment%20to%20that%20bleak%2C%20early-winter%20day%20in%20Munich%20one%20hundred%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnjan%20Basu%20is%20a%20literary%20critic%2C%20commentator%20and%20translator%20based%20out%20of%20Bangalore.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20basuanjan52%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699519681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F16095947%2FHitler_salute_in_front_of_lamppost.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fthe-watershed-moment-in-german-history-that-created-adolf-hitler%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22That%20tipping%20point%20that%20led%20to%20Hitler's%20rise%20was%20a%20set%20of%20extraordinary%20events%20that%20played%20out%20in%20Munich%20exactly%20one%20100%20years%20ago%20today%2C%20on%20November%209%2C%201923.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fthe-watershed-moment-in-german-history-that-created-adolf-hitler%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra%20Victim%20Of%20Politics%2C%20Can%20Fight%20On%20Her%20Own%3A%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20party%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20accused%20of%20taking%20money%20from%20a%20prominent%20businessman%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament.%20Calling%20the%20Krishnanagar%20MP%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictim%20of%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20the%20firebrand%20leader%20is%20%26quot%3Bcompetent%20enough%20to%20fight%20her%20own%20battles%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20targeting%20Trinamool%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20this%20step%20by%20the%20central%20government%20and%20what%20I%20read%20of%20the%20ehtics%20committee%20report%2C%20they%20have%20said%20an%20investigation%20should%20happen%20against%20her.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20have%20anything%20against%20Mahua%20(Moitra)%20and%20it%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20investigation%2C%20then%20why%20has%20an%20expulsion%20been%20recommended.%20I%20feel%20Mahua%20is%20competent%20enought%20to%20fight%20her%20battles%20on%20her%20own.%20They%20are%20victimising%20me%20for%20four%20years%20too%2C%20it%20is%20their%20standard%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20first%20remarks%20by%20Mr%20Banerjee%2C%20considered%20the%20Number%202%20in%20Trinamool%20at%20this%20point%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra%20case.%20His%20remarks%20are%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Trinamool's%20caution%20in%20commenting%20on%20the%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20party%2C%20which%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20of%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20and%20other%20institutions%20to%20target%20political%20rivals%2C%20has%20been%20conscipicuosly%20silent%20in%20its%20remarks%20in%20this%20matter%20and%20has%20largely%20left%20Ms%20Moitra%20to%20fight%20her%20case%20as%20several%20issues%20from%20her%20personal%20life%20have%20dominated%20the%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20addressed%20the%20media%20several%20times%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20has%20not%20spoken%20at%20all%20about%20the%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%20Earlier%2C%20party%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Bhas%20nothing%20to%20say%20on%20this%20issue%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20person%20around%20whom%20this%20controversy%20is%20revolving%20is%20best%20suited%20to%20react%20to%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDerek%20O'Brien%2C%20Trinamool's%20leader%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leadership%20will%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision%20in%20the%20matter%20after%20the%20Parliamentary%20panel%20probing%20the%20matter%20completes%20its%20investigation%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20member%20concerned%20has%20been%20advised%20by%20the%20party%20leadership%20to%20clarify%20her%20position%20regarding%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20her.%20She%20has%20already%20done%20that.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20matter%20has%20to%20do%20with%20an%20elected%20MP%2C%20her%20rights%20and%20privileges%2C%20let%20the%20matter%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20right%20forum%20of%20Parliament%2C%20after%20which%20the%20party%20leadership%20will%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20receiving%20cash%20and%20expensive%20gifts%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20accessed%20the%20report%20by%20the%20Parliamentary%20ethics%20committee%20examining%20the%20matter.%20Calling%20Ms%20Moitra's%20actions%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20objectionable%2C%20unethical%2C%20heinous%20and%20criminal%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20panel%20has%20said%20she%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20as%20an%20MP%20and%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20membership%20should%20be%20terminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20money%20trail%20of%20cash%20transaction%20between%20Smt%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20Shri%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20'quid%20pro%20quo'%20should%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20in%20a%20legal%2C%20institutional%20and%20time-bound%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20who%20complained%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20yesterday%20said%20anti-corruption%20body%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20basis%20of%20my%20complaint%2C%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20corruption%20that%20compromises%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20accepted%20cash%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%20on%20his%20behalf%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20business%20rival%20Adani%20Group.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20by%20sharing%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20with%20the%20businessman%2C%20had%20compromised%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20regulation%20regaring%20the%20sharing%20of%20login%20and%20password.%20Earlier%2C%20she%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20ethics%20panel%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20asked%20%26quot%3Bfilthy%20questions%26quot%3B.%20Opposition%20MPs%20on%20the%20panel%20had%20also%20questioned%20how%20the%20meeting%20was%20conducted%20and%20staged%20a%20walkout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MPs%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20including%20its%20chairman%20Vinod%20Sonkar%2C%20accused%20Ms%20Moitra%20of%20not%20cooperating%20in%20the%20probe%20and%20walking%20out%20to%20avoid%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699519380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F9nlk07l8_mahua-abhishek-split_625x300_09_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-a-victim-of-politics-says-trinamool-mp-abhishek-banerjee-4559876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20party%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20accused%20of%20taking%20money%20from%20a%20prominent%20businessman%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament.%22%