%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20rally%20was%20attended%20by%20senior%20leaders%20including%20the%20Left%20Font%20chairman%20Biman%20Basu%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%20Bengal%20state%20secretary%20Mohammad%20Selim%20and%20the%20former%20Bengal%20state%20secretary%2C%20Surjya%20Kanta%20Mishra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20march%20in%20Kolkata%20was%20a%20powerful%20display%20of%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20and%20a%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20the%20violence.%20Protesters%20demanded%20that%20the%20United%20States%20take%20action%20to%20stop%20the%20Israeli%20massacre%20and%20ensure%20a%20ceasefire.%20They%20also%20called%20for%20an%20end%20to%20all%20aid%20and%20support%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20jointly%20by%20CPI(M)%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPI%20(ML)%20Liberation%2C%20RSP%2C%20AIFB%2C%20MFB%20and%20the%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Party%2C%20the%20Left%20parties%20criticised%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20the%20US-Israeli%20military%20operation%20in%20Palestine%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98de%20facto%20approval%20of%20the%20US-Israeli%20genocide%E2%80%99.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20impending%20visit%20by%20the%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20and%20Defence%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20to%20India%2C%20Left%20supporters%20will%20observe%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20across%20all%20the%20district%20headquarters%20of%20the%20state%20on%20Friday%2C%20November%2010%20from%202%20pm%20to%204%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20the%20crowd%20before%20the%20march%2C%20the%20Left%20Front%20chairman%20Bose%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20world%20is%20protesting.%20Protests%20are%20taking%20place%20all%20over%20the%20Western%20world.%20Kolkata%20has%20an%20anti-imperialist%20tradition.%20We%20are%20partner%20in%20the%20liberation%20struggle%20of%20Palestine.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%