%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsncr.com%2Fnational%2Fwhat-is-the-need-of-raiding-the-same-house-5-times-sharad-pawars-allegation-bjp-is-misusing-ed-cbi-and-ncb%2F%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20years%20ago%3A%20What%20was%20the%20need%20for%20different%20agencies%20to%20raid%20the%20same%20house%20five%20times%3F%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20raids%20on%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Nawab%20Malik.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20late%2C%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%20and%20IT%20department%20have%20become%20more%20brash%20and%20ruthless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20previous%20ED%20chief%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%20finally%20left%2C%20he%20could%20claim%20credit%20for%20two%20solid%20achievements%3A%20scaring%20and%20silencing%20Mayawati%20and%20splitting%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20thus%20giving%20birth%20to%20the%20present%20ruling%20coalition%20there.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20FIRs%20and%20cases%20against%20several%20NCP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20defectors%2C%20including%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20Praful%20Patel%20and%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharashtra-politics-ajit-pawar-hasan-mushrif-chaggan-bhujbal-praful-patel-ncp-mlas-ed-cbi-scanner-17102581.htm%5C%22%3Eallegedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%20in%20a%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20scam%20and%20Patel%20in%20money%20laundering%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDefection%20to%20the%20BJP%20side%20has%20given%20them%20protection%20from%20prosecution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20ED%20chief%20Rahul%20Navin%20has%20begun%20in%20earnest.%20Monitored%20by%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20pre-poll%20raids%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20have%20been%20launched%20on%20a%20much%20bigger%20scale%20on%20firms%20and%20individuals%20close%20to%20the%20opposition%20