-agencies-latest-trick-opposition-leaders%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSome%20Misused%20It%26quot%3B%3A%20Omegle%20Founder%20On%20Why%20Site%20Is%20Shutting%20Down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20online%20chat%20platform%20Omegle%20has%20officially%20shut%20down%20after%20a%2014-year%20run.%20Introduced%20in%202009%2C%20this%20free%20service%20was%20known%20for%20randomly%20matching%20users%20for%20anonymous%20one-on-one%20conversations.%20With%20the%20primary%20goal%20of%20connecting%20strangers%20and%20facilitating%20interactions%20with%20other%20people%20online%2C%20Omegle%20played%20a%20unique%20role%20in%20providing%20a%20platform%20for%20users%20to%20meet%20new%20users%20in%20a%20virtual%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20Omegle%20shutting%20down%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFounder%20Leif%20K-Brooks%20cited%20the%20substantial%20costs%20of%20managing%20Omegle%20and%20addressing%20potential%20misuse%20as%20the%20primary%20reasons%20behind%20the%20site's%20shutdown.%20He%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20much%20as%20I%20wish%20circumstances%20were%20different%2C%20the%20stress%20and%20expense%20of%20this%20fight%20%E2%80%93%20coupled%20with%20the%20existing%20stress%20and%20expense%20of%20operating%20Omegle%2C%20and%20fighting%20its%20misuse%20%E2%80%93%20are%20simply%20too%20much.%20Operating%20Omegle%20is%20no%20longer%20sustainable%2C%20financially%20nor%20psychologically.%E2%80%9D%20If%20you%20visit%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omegle.com%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3EOmegle%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%2C%20you%20will%20see%20a%20tombstone%20reading%2C%20%E2%80%9COmegle%202009-2023.%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.omegle.com%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1699602081442000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1oOAzUVj7