Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fomegle-popular-video-chat-site-shuts-down-after-14-years-4559885%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Omegle%20shuts%20down%20after%2014%20years%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20the%20founder%20has%20to%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699517358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105090161%2Cimgsize-808419.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fread-omegle-shuts-down-after-14-years-heres-what-the-founder-has-to-say%2Farticleshow%2F105090190.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Omegle%2C%20the%20anonymous%20online%20chat%20platform%20that%20allowed%20users%20to%20interact%20with%20strangers%20without%20revealing%20personal%20information%2C%20has%20shut%20down%20after%2014%20years.%20The%20founder%2C%20Leif%20K-Brooks%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20stress%20and%20expense%20of%20operating%20the%20website%20and%20dealing%20with%20misuse%20became%20overwhelming.%20Omegle%20gained%20popularity%20for%20its%20unique%20concept%20of%20randomly%20connecting%20users%20in%20chat%20sessions.%20While%20the%20site%20had%20positive%20experiences%20and%20even%20helped%20law%20enforcement%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20it%20also%20faced%20criticism%20for%20its%20misuse.%20K-Brooks%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20urged%20support%20for%20organizations%20fighting%20for%20online%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fread-omegle-shuts-down-after-14-years-heres-what-the-founder-has-to-say%2Farticleshow%2F105090190.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Controlling%20Pollution%20Through%20Cloud%20Seeding%20Is%20Not%20A%20Permanent%20Solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20the%20rising%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20use%20artificial%20rain%20through%20cloud%20seeding.%20The%20mechanism%20is%20being%20developed%20by%20researchers%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%2C%20Kanpur.%20%C2%A0Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20met%20with%20a%20team%20from%20IIT%20Kanpur%20on%20November%208%20to%20discuss%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20cloud%20seeding.%20He%20informed%20that%20Delhi%20might%20experience%20artificial%20rainfall%20if%20the%20skies%20of%20the%20city%20remain%20cloudy%20on%20November%2020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Manindra%20Agrawal%20from%20Department%20of%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20at%20IIT%20Kanpur%20shared%20some%20insights%20on%20the%20working%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIT%20Kanpur%20has%20its%20own%20aircraft%20that%20has%20been%20attached%20with%20flares%20for%20implementing%20cloud%20seeding.%20We%20have%20also%20received%20approval%20from%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20for%20the%20flares%20and%20aircraft.%20We%20can%20now%20carry%20on%20with%20the%20process%20of%20cloud%20seeding%20to%20create%20artificial%20rain%20wherever%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Prof%20Agrawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIT%20Kanpur%20has%20been%20working%20and%20planning%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry%20(CII)%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months%20to%20introduce%20measures%20and%20steps%20for%20curbing%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20region%20with%20the%20help%20of%20cloud%20seeding%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Prof%20Agarwal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20recently%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20institute%20multiple%20times%20to%20seek%20help%20for%20creating%20artificial%20rain%20in%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20efficiency%20of%20the%20process%2C%20the%20professor%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CCountering%20or%20controlling%20pollution%20through%20cloud%20seeding%20is%20not%20a%20permanent%20solution.%20It%20is%20a%20temporary%20process%20and%20lasts%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%20two%20weeks.%20The%20dust%20particles%20present%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20are%20washed%20away%20in%20the%20artificial%20rains%20created%20and%20gets%20settled%20in%20the%20soil%20making%20the%20environment%20pollution-free.%20The%20process%20will%20result%20in%20a%20temporary%20relief%20to%20the%20people.%20Also%2C%20the%20artificial%20rains%20can%20be%20formed%20only%20at%20places%20where%20clouds%20are%20present.%20To%20eliminate%20pollution%20permanently%20from%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20we%20must%20try%20and%20work%20on%20introducing%20measures%20to%20counter%20the%20sources%20of%20pollution%20in%20the%20atmosphere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20NCR%20region%20is%20spread%20over%20an%20area%20of%20more%20than%201%2C000%20square%20kilometres%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20institute%20will%20therefore%20require%20to%20do%20cloud%20seeding%20in%20a%20very%20large%20area.%20He%20also%20explained%20that%20creation%20of%20artificial%20rains%20depends%20on%20the%20presence%20and%20kind%20of%20clouds%20in%20a%20region%20which%20is%20not%20under%20human%20control.%20The%20cost%20of%20the%20entire%20process%20is%20quite%20expensive%20as%20the%20aircraft%20charges%2C%20its%20fuel%20maintenance%2C%20flares%20are%20a%20bit%20costly.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699517280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fair-pollution-in-delhi_625x300_1529041941478.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontrolling-pollution-through-cloud-seeding-is-not-a-permanent-solution-says-iit-kanpur-professor-4559962%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20met%20with%20a%20team%20from%20IIT%20Kanpur%20on%20November%208%20to%20discuss%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20cloud%20seeding%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%22%2C%22au