%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20left%20it%20to%20the%20High%20Courts%20of%20each%20state%20(in%20which%20the%20case%20is%20being%20heard)%20to%20monitor%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20frame%20uniform%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20for%20the%20second%20-%20regarding%20electoral%20ban%20on%20convicted%20persons%20-%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20also%20asked%20no%20adjournments%20be%20given%20%26quot%3Bexcept%20in%20rare%20and%20exceptional%20circumstances%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20in%20case%20of%20delays%20bail%20be%20cancelled.%20Trial%20courts%20have%20now%20told%20not%20to%20adjourn%20cases%20unless%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20was%20made%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%202015%20judgement%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20said%20%26quot%3B...%20in%20relation%20to%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%2C%20who%20have%20charges%20framed%20against%20them...%20the%20trial%20shall%20be%20concluded%20speedily...%20and%2C%20in%20no%20case%2C%20later%20than%20one%20year%20from%20date%20of%20framing%20of%20charge(s)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-to-hear-plea-on-speedy-trial-against-mps-mlas-soon-nearly-5-000-cases-pending-2870271%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20To%20Hear%20Plea%20On%20Trial%20Against%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%2C%20Nearly%205%2C000%20Cases%20Pending%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%20said%3A%20%26quot%3B...%20as%20far%20as%20possible%2C%20trial%20shall%20be%20on%20day-to-day%20basis.%20If%2C%20for%20some%20extraordinary%20circumstances%2C%20court%20is%20not%20able%20to%20conclude%20trial%20within%20one%20year...%20(it%20will)%20submit%20report%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20respective%20High%20Court%2C%20indicating%20reasons%20for%20not%20adhering%20to%20time%20limit...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20compliance%20with%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20in%20this%20case%2C%20various%20High%20Courts%20had%20reported%20the%20number%20of%20pending%20cases%20(as%20of%20December%202018%20and%20November%202022)%20against%20MPs%20and%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20these%20numbers%2C%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20such%20pending%20cases%20are%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20992%20unresolved%20cases%20in%202018.%20Last%20year%20this%20number%20was%201%2C377%2C%20and%20719%20of%20these%20had%20been%20undecided%20for%20over%20five%20years.%20Among%20the%20larger%20states%2C%20others%20with%20such%20high%20numbers%20are%20Bihar%3B%20there%20were%20546%20pending%20cases%20as%20of%20November%20and%20381%20have%20been%20in%20limbo%20for%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20data%20other%20states%20with%20over%20100%20cases%20pending%20for%20over%20five%20years%20are%20Maharashtra%20(169)%20and%20Odisha%20(323)%2C%20while%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%2060%2C%20Karnataka%2061%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2051%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%2072.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699510920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fgv8pfg28_supreme-court_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-cases-against-mps-mlas-mlcs-special-benches-no-delays-supreme-court-on-cases-against-mps-mlas-4559623%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20re-directed%20High%20Courts%20to%20initiate%20suo%20moto%20proceedings%20for%20speedy%20disposal%20of%20pending%20cas