mitments%20made%20to%20the%20ITLF%20in%20August%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20those%20commitments%20have%20either%20been%20reneged%20upon%20or%20not%20fulfilled%20in%20proper%20spirit.%20Vualzong%20did%20accept%20that%20this%20is%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%9Chope%20against%20hope%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5PWd_0B3Zu0%3Fsi%3DVW-8f7vJdovs0fQU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20weeks%20of%20relative%20calm%20in%20Manipur%2C%20when%20many%20came%20to%20believe%20the%20situation%20was%20improving%2C%20the%20ITLF%20press%20release%20declaring%20that%20faith%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20waning%20day%20by%20day%20is%20an%20ominous%20and%20worrying%20note%2C%20particularly%20because%20it%20happens%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20been%20an%20uptick%20in%20killings%20and%20abductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Vualzong%20discusses%20all%20the%20demands%20made%20by%20the%20ITLF%20in%20August%20to%20Shah%2C%20and%20the%20response%20and%20commitments%20given%20by%20the%20government.%20In%20each%20case%2C%20he%20explains%20where%20the%20government%20has%20fallen%20short%20in%20fulfilling%20its%20promises%20as%20well%20as%20the%20one%20issue%20on%20which%20it%20has%20taken%20action%20%E2%80%93%20although%20inadequately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVualzong%20also%20raises%20a%20new%20issue%20i.e.%20the%20discriminatory%20response%20of%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20to%20atrocities%20committed%20on%20the%20Meiteis%20compared%20to%20its%20response%20to%20atrocities%20committed%20on%20the%20Kukis.%20This%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20arisen%20after%20the%20August%20talks%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20critical%20Kuki-Zo%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%2C%20Vualzong%20says%20the%20talks%20are%20effectively%20stalled%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20progress%20since%20August.%20He%20agrees%20and%20accepts%20that%20this%20is%20perhaps%20because%20the%20government%20came%20to%20believe%20that%20because%20Manipur%20was%20relatively%20calm%20during%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20and%20the%20government%20could%20afford%20to%20drag%20its%20feet%20in%20the%20hope%20the%20matter%20would%20resolve%20itself%20without%20further%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699510822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09112902%2Fkt-9-nov-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwatch-trust-in-modi-government-is-waning-day-by-day-kuki-itlf-spokesperson%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20Ginza%20Vualzong%20added%20that%20the%20ITKF%20and%20the%20wider%20Kuki%20community%20still%20have%20%E2%80%9Ca%20flicker%20of%20hope%E2%80%9D%20and%20they%20%E2%80%9Cpray%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20fulfil%20the%20commitments%20it%20has%20made.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwatch-trust-in-modi-government-is-waning-day-by-day-kuki-itlf-spokesperson%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Genpact%20CEO%20'Tiger'%20Tyagarajan%20announces%20retirement%2C%20B%20K%20Kalra%20to%20take%20over%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699510795000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-06%2F03%2Ffull%2F1591205619-8947.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgenpact-ceo-tiger-tyagarajan-announces-retirement-b-k-kalra-to-take-over-123110900339_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kalra%20presently%20leads%20business%20transformation%20at%20the%20