odification%20technique%20where%20substances%20are%20introduced%20into%20clouds%20to%20encourage%20precipitation.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20cloud%20seeding%20for%20rain%2C%20common%20substances%20like%20silver%20iodide%20or%20potassium%20iodide%20are%20dispersed%20into%20the%20clouds%20using%20aeroplanes%20or%20helicopters.%20These%20particles%20serve%20as%20nuclei%20around%20which%20water%20droplets%20can%20form%2C%20eventually%20leading%20to%20the%20development%20of%20raindrops.%20The%20process%20typically%20takes%20around%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20but%20its%20success%20depends%20on%20specific%20meteorological%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20presence%20of%20moisture-laden%20clouds%20and%20suitable%20wind%20patterns.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20enhance%20rainfall%20in%20specific%20areas%20or%20alleviate%20drought%20conditions.%20It's%20a%20fascinating%20method%20used%20to%20influence%20weather%20patterns%20for%20agricultural%2C%20environmental%2C%20or%20water%20resource%20management%20purposes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDelhi%2C%20today%2C%20has%20an%20AQI%20of%20670%2C%20which%20is%20extremely%20%E2%80%9Chazardous%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faqicn.org%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%C2%A0%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Air%20Pollution%20Board%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Pollutants%20like%20fine%20particulate%20matter%20(PM2.5%20and%20PM10)%2C%20nitrogen%20dioxide%20(NO2)%2C%20sulfur%20dioxide%20(SO2)%2C%20and%20others%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20well%20above%20safe%20limits%2C%20contributing%20to%20respiratory%20issues%2C%20cardiovascular%20problems%2C%20and%20other%20health%20complications.%20Vulnerable%20populations%2C%20such%20as%20children%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20individuals%20with%20pre-existing%20health%20conditions%2C%20are%20particularly%20at%20risk.%20Breathing%20in%20the%20polluted%20air%20in%20Delhi%20is%20said%20to%20be%20like%20smoking%20around%2010%20cigarettes%20a%20day%2C%20according%20to%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20tackle%20the%20issue%20by%20implementing%20measures%20like%20the%20odd-even%20scheme%20for%20vehicles%2C%20closing%20schools%20for%20in-person%20classes%2C%20and%20following%20Stage%20IV%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP).%20However%2C%20experts%20are%20warning%20that%20things%20might%20get%20even%20worse%20during%20Diwali%20due%20to%20firecrackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699508460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F7ohqig2o_delhi-pollution-sondeep_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhis-air-quality-what-is-artificial-rain-and-how-will-it-help-reduce-pollution-in-delhi-4559413%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20use%20artificial%20rain%20through%20cloud%20seeding%20this%20month%20to%20tackle%20the%20high%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhis-air-quality-what-is-artificial-rain-and-how-will-it-help-reduce-pollution-in-delhi-4559413%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhis-air-quality-what-is-artificial-rain-and-how-will-it-help-reduce-pollution-in-delhi-4559413%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhis-air-quality-what-is-artificial-rain-and-how-will-it-help-reduce-pollution-in-delhi-4559413%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Leo'%20BO%3A%20Vijay%20starrer%20reaches%20Rs%20600%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699508002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105085894%2Cimgsize-63610.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%