ccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20of%20the%2070.24%20crore%20PAN%20card%20holders%20in%20India%2C%2057.25%20crore%20have%20linked%20their%20cards%20with%20Aadhaar.%20Among%20the%20nearly%2013%20crore%20who%20have%20not%2C%2011.5%20crore%20cards%20have%20been%20deactivated%2C%20the%20RTI%20reply%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20were%20issued%20PAN%20cards%20after%20July%201%2C%202017%2C%20the%20linking%20with%20Aadhaar%20was%20done%20automatically.%20But%20those%20who%20were%20issued%20PAN%20cards%20before%20that%20date%20had%20to%20link%20it%20manually%2C%20under%20sub-section%20(2)%20of%20Section%20139AA%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20linking%20of%20PAN%20and%20Aadhaar%20was%20required%20to%20be%20done%20on%20or%20before%20a%20notified%20date%2C%20failing%20which%20PAN%20becomes%20inoperative%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CBDT%20said%20in%20the%20RTI%20reply%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20234H%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%20also%20makes%20a%20person%20who%20has%20not%20linked%20their%20PAN%20with%20Aadhaar%20liable%20to%20pay%20a%20fee.%20To%20get%20the%20PAN%20card%20reactivated%2C%20the%20CBDT%20has%20imposed%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%201%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaur%20criticised%20this%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20new%20PAN%20card%20is%20Rs%2091%20excluding%20GST.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20how%20can%20the%20government%20impose%20a%2010-fold%20fine%20for%20getting%20the%20PAN%20card%20reactivated%3F%20Also%2C%20how%20will%20people%20whose%20PAN%20cards%20have%20gotten%20deactivated%20file%20income%20tax%3F%20Government%20should%20rethink%20and%20extend%20time%20limits%20for%20at%20least%20a%20year%20for%20linking%20PAN%20with%20Aadhaar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaur%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699507845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09120730%2FAadhaar-cards.jpg%22%2C%22or