ge%20incurred%20by%20yami%20baito%20crime%20rings%20and%20other%20organised%20fraudsters%20soared%2030%20percent%20from%20the%20previous%20year%20to%20top%2037%20billion%20yen%20(around%20%24250%20million)%2C%20the%20first%20increase%20in%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGateway%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlack-market%20job%20advertisements%20have%20long%20appeared%20in%20Japanese%20magazines%20or%20on%20stickers%20in%20public%20toilets.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20thanks%20to%20their%20proliferation%20online%2C%20recruiters%20now%20can%20%26quot%3Bjust%20relax%20in%20an%20air-conditioned%20room%2C%20sip%20coffee%20and%20use%20your%20mobile%20to%20assemble%20a%20group%20of%20robbers%2C%26quot%3B%20criminal%20sociologist%20Noboru%20Hirosue%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnline%20platforms%2C%20especially%20encrypted%20messaging%20apps%20like%20Telegram%20and%20Signal%2C%20also%20help%20gangs%20remain%20nameless%20and%20untraceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2057-year-old%20former%20yami%20baito%20hiree%20described%20how%20his%20supervisor%20would%20direct%20him%20via%20Telegram%20to%20drop%20parcels%20of%20illicit%20cash%20in%20train%20station%20lockers%20in%20Tokyo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20you're%20in%20a%20video%20game%2C%20where%20you're%20given%20tasks%2C%20complete%20missions%20and%20get%20rewards%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20man%2C%20who%20spent%20time%20in%20jail%20but%20now%20works%20at%20a%20hostel%2C%20said%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20each%20day%2C%20anonymous%20Telegram%20messages%20with%20emojis%20would%20thank%20him%20for%20his%20work%20and%20tell%20him%20where%20his%20day's%20pay%20lay%20hidden%2C%20waiting%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20even%20feel%20guilty%20because%20you%20don't%20see%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChampagne%20celebrations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20a%2090-year-old%20Tokyo%20woman%20died%20after%20being%20tied%20up%20and%20beaten%20in%20her%20house%20by%20several%20men%20looking%20for%20valuables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20assault%2C%20which%20shocked%20Japan%20and%20focused%20police%20attention%20on%20the%20problem%20of%20yami%20baito%20crimes%2C%20had%20reportedly%20been%20hired%20through%20online%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kingpins%20were%20a%20Philippines-based%20gang%20of%20Japanese%20men%2C%20who%20reportedly%20used%20Telegram%20to%20direct%20a%20team%20of%20underlings%20who%20carried%20out%20break-ins%20and%20fraud%20schemes%20across%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20hired%20to%20go%20into%20crime%20have%20varying%20reasons%20for%20doing%20so.%20But%20for%20a%2031-year-old%20former%20low-ranking%20member%20of%20an%20organised%20fraud%20group%2C%20it%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bearn%20extra%20money%20so%20I%20can%20go%20a%20bit%20crazy%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonning%20a%20suit%2C%20he%20would%20pose%20as%20a%20bank%20official%20and%20visit%20the%20homes%20of%20elderly%20people%2C%20convincing%20them%20to%20hand%20over%20their%20cash%20cards.%20The%20gig%20earned%20him%20nearly%2010%20million%20yen%20(%2466%2C000)%20in%20just%20a%20few%20months%2C%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20could%20think%20about%20was%20I%20could%20get%20wasted%20again%20that%20night...%20drinking%20expensive%20champagne%20at%20hostess%20bars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20eventually%20jailed%20for%20two%20years.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExploited%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20been%20scrambling%20to%20get%20criminal%20ads%20taken%20down%20and%20have%20offered%20rewards%20of%20up%20to%201%20million%20yen%20(about%20%246%2C600)%20for%20information%20on%20the%20gangs%20behind%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriminal%20recruits%20are%20being%20%26quot%3Bexploited%20and%20disposed%20of%20as%20pawns%26quot%3B