upplements%20and%20coordinates%20their%20efforts%20in%20several%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20efforts%20include%20providing%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPFs)%3B%20sanction%20of%20India%20Reserve%20(IR)%20battalions%3B%20setting%20up%20of%20Counter%20Insurgency%20and%20Anti-Terrorism%20(CIAT)%20schools%3B%20modernisation%20and%20upgradation%20of%20the%20State%20Police%20and%20their%20Intelligence%20apparatus%3B%20reimbursement%20of%20security-related%20expenditure%20under%20the%20Security-related%20Expenditure%20(SRE)%20Scheme%3B%20providing%20helicopters%2C%20training%2C%20sharing%20intelligence%2C%20facilitating%20inter-state%20coordination%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20underlying%20philosophy%20is%20to%20enhance%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20State%20Governments%20to%20tackle%20the%20Maoist%20menace%20in%20a%20concerted%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699455928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08202949%2FF-UafbcXsAAQmL5.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-narendra-modi-congress-naxal-violence-union-government-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20look%20at%20the%20home%20ministry's%20data%20on%20reduction%20of%20Maoist%20violence%20over%20the%20years%20belies%20the%20prime%20minister's%20claims%20of%20increase%20in%20Maoist%20violence%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-narendra-modi-congress-naxal-violence-union-government-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20documents%20seen%20by%20Sky%20News%20show%20Italy's%20migrant%20deal%20with%20Albania%20is%20far%20less%20radical%20than%20UK's%20Rwanda