20but%20was%20met%20with%20rejections%20and%20no%20explanations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20gone%20through%20tests%2C%20given%20all%20my%20papers%20and%20documents%2C%20handed%20it%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20and%20they%20denied%20it%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20me%20an%20explanation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20that%E2%80%99s%20very%20painful.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20wrong%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20disability%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20health%20condition%2C%20and%20so%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185510%2Fimage-1487.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22606%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185510%2Fimage-1487.png%20606w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185510%2Fimage-1487-220x300.png%20220w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20for%20assistive%20technology%20like%20Ali%E2%80%99s%20wheelchair%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Ftools%2Fata-toolkit%5C%22%3EThe%20WHO%20Global%20Report%20on%20Assistive%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%202.5%20billion%20people%20globally%20require%20assistive%20technology.%20It%20said%20that%20while%20data%20is%20limited%2C%20in%20Africa%20and%20Asia%2C%20surveys%20showed%20largely%20unmet%20needs%2C%20ranging%20from%2025%25%20to%20over%2090%25%20due%20to%20high%20costs%2C%20lack%20of%20financing%2C%20availability%2C%20awareness%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20trained%20personnel.%20These%20unmet%20needs%20are%20only%20heightened%20by%20the%20difficulty%20in%20getting%20assistive%20technology%20insured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20finally%20secured%20insurance%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20coverage%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Fstar-health-and-allied-insurance-co--ltd%2F%5C%22%3EStar%20Health%20and%20Allied%20Insurance%20Co.%20Ltd%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20private%20insurance%20company%2C%20and%20got%20his%20wheelchair%20insured%20under%20the%20all-risk%20cover%20policy%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Fsbigeneral%2F%5C%22%3ESBI%20General%20Insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20coverage%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmomentous%20step%20forward%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20his%20insurance%20would%20cover%20his%20assistive%20technology%20needs%20and%20services%20like%20rehabilitation%20and%20physiotherapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20gaining%20insurance%20for%20his%20wheelchair%20instils%20hope%20and%20inspiration%20for%20the%20millions%20of%20people%20with%20disabilities%20and%20elderly%20people%20who%20use%20a%20variety%20of%20assistive%20devices%20for%20their%20activities%20of%20daily%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20sent%20emails%20and%20letters%20to%20the%20managing%20directors%20and%20CEOs%20of%2026%20public%20and%20private%20general%20insurance%20companies%2C%20but%20received%20no%20response%20from%20almost%2040%25%20of%20the%20companies.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20received%20an%20offer%20from%20SBI%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoor%20response%20from%20government%20hospitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20that%20discrimination%20in%20accessing%20healthcare%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20terms%20of%20response%2C%20government%20insurance%20companies%20perform%20the%20poorest.%20They%20did%20not%20get%20back%20to%20him%20despite%20multiple%20follow-ups%20from%20other%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20despite%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20saying%20that%20insurance%20products%20should%20be%20designed%20to%20enable%20people%20with%20disabilities%20to%20obtain%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20and%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20cannot%20be%20discriminated%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20he%20hopes%20to%20instil%20hope%20among%20many%20people%20by%20sharing%20the%20news%20of%20his%20health%20insurance%20coverage.%20He%20believes%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20acute%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20disabled%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20navigate%20the%20process%20of%20obtaining%20insurance%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20huge%20cost%20for%20the%20families%20and%20disabled%20people%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20this%20lack%20of%20understanding%20extends%20to%20insurance%20companies%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20to%20build%20awareness%20%5Bon%20insurance%20products%20for%20disabled%20people%5D%2C%20and%20the%20government%20should%20also%20incentivise%20or%20come%20up%20with%20schemes%20that%20include%20all%20people%20with%20disabilities%20under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20challenges%20around%20understanding%20blood%20disorders%20and%20insurance%20will%20not%20be%20resolved%20until%20and%20unless%20we%20build%20our%20understanding%20around%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20NCPEDP%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20and%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20(IRDAI)%20held%20a%20stakeholders%20consultation%20with%20disability%20advocacy%20organisations%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20he%20said%20both%20private%20and%20government%20insurance%20companies%20were%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699452032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185756%2Fimage-1488.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisabled-people-india-securing-health-insurance-difficult-task%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Securing%20health%20insurance%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20toward%20affordability.%20But%20in%20India%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20disability%2C%20the%20more%20difficult%20it%20becomes%20to%20gain%20insurance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisabled-people-india-securing-health-insurance-difficult-task%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paramilitary%20Veterans%20Demand%20Restoration%20of%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20Knock%20at%20PM%20Modi's%20Door%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27135014%2FScreenshot-2023-09-27-at-1.36.28-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Confederation%20of%20Ex-Paramilitary%20Forces%20Welfare%20Associations%20has%20sought%20the%20appointment%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20press%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(OPS)%20and%20appraise%20him%20of%20their%20longstanding%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20OPS%20has%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20following%20several%20protests%20and%20widespread%20discontent%20among%20the%2012%20lakh%20serving%20and%20eight%20lakh%20retired%20paramilitary%20personnel%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20November%206%2C%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Ex-Paramilitary%20Forces%20Welfare%20Associations%E2%80%99%20national%20coordinator%20Ranbir%20Singh%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20association%20had%20sent%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20requesting%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20PM.%20He%20highlighted%20the%20fact%20that%20paramilitary%20personnel%20often%20perform%20duties%20in%20hostile%20terrains%20and%20safeguard%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20borders%20alongside%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Despite%20their%20significant%20contributions%2C%20they%20have%20been%20clubbed%20with%20civilian%20counterparts%20under%20the%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NPS)%2C%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cdiscriminatory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20this%20discrimination%20to%20end%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20have%20sought%20an%20appointment%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fex-paramilitary-body-seeks-meeting-with-pm-modi-over-demand-to-restore-old-pension-scheme%2Fcid%2F1978385%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20personnel%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%2C%20have%20long%20felt%20neglected%20and%20discriminated%20against%20in%20comparison%20to%20their%20counterparts%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20introduce%20the%20NPS%20in%202004%20replaced%20the%20regular%20pension%20scheme%20for%20paramilitary%20jawans%2C%20placing%20them%20in%20a%20contributory%20system%20that%20many%20argue%20is%20unfair%20and%20inadequate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECore%20demands%3A%20Pension%20restoration%20and%20pay%20parity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20demand%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20Confederation%20is%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20OPS%20for%20paramilitary%20personnel%2C%20a%20benefit%20currently%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20army%2C%20navy%2C%20and%20air%20force.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20association%20is%20pressing%20for%20salaries%20equivalent%20to%20those%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20for%20serving%20paramilitary%20personnel.%20This%20would%20address%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20pay%20scales%2C%20where%20paramilitary%20personnel%20receive%20significantly%20lower%20salaries%20for%20their%20risk-prone%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famrit-kaal-and-the-two-types-of-retired-old-men%5C%22%3EAmrit%20Kaal%20and%20the%20Two%20Types%20of%20Retired%20Old%20Men%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20association%20is%20seeking%20an%20exemption%20from%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20at%20central%20police%20canteens%2C%20aligning%20it%20with%20the%20privileges%20offered%20to%20the%20defense%20forces.%20These%20demands%20underscore%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20bridge%20the%20existing%20gaps%20and%20treat%20paramilitary%20personnel%20with%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20and%20frustration%3A%20The%20battle%20for%20recognition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20veterans%20have%20been%20vocal%20about%20their%20grievances%2C%20staging%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20their%20plight.%20Their%20past%20protests%2C%20including%20one%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famrit-kaal-and-the-two-types-of-retired-old-men%5C%22%3ESeptember%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20highlighted%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20policy%20reforms%20and%20fair%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20veterans%20have%20highlighted%20the%20discriminatory%20practices%20that%20have%20persisted%20for%20years.%20They%20have%20been%20part%20of%20crucial%20battles%2C%20including%20the%201965%2C%201971%2C%20and%201999%20Kargil%20wars%2C%20standing%20alongside%20the%20army%20as%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence.%20Despite%20their%20sacrifices%20and%20contributions%2C%20they%20say%2C%20their%20pension%20benefits%20have%20been%20curtailed%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20discontent%20and%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fparamilitary-forces-armed-forces-of-union-old-pension-scheme-applicable-to-personnel