ive%20%E2%80%98Volanity%E2%80%99%20launched%20in%202021%20is%20a%20step%20towards%20structuring%20the%20volunteering%20space%20in%20Delhi%20while%20also%20integrating%20holistic%20education%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20Taarush%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332810%2Fkota-suicides-iit-jee-neet-coaching-classes-entrance-exams-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhole%20new%20world%20of%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20lay%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20academics.%20His%20grandfather%20is%20to%20thank.%20As%20the%20latter%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20time%20teaching%20kids%20in%20Dhatir%2C%20Faridabad%2C%20Taarush%20would%20accompany%20him%2C%20watch%20and%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20topics%20taught%20were%20seldom%20things%20you%E2%80%99d%20find%20in%20books.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20the%20Delhi%20boy%E2%80%99s%20fondness%20for%20life%20lessons%20took%20root.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20left%20since%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20was%20the%20pandemic%20that%20provoked%20tangible%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fvolunteering--1699274534.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taarush%20has%20been%20volunteering%20at%20NGOs%20across%20Delhi%20ever%20since%20he%20was%20ten%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fvolunteering--1699274534.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fvolunteering--1699274534-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fvolunteering--1699274534-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fvolunteeri