0in%20Assam.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20present%2C%20the%2034-year-old%20proudly%20owns%20his%20own%20enterprise%2C%20Daily%20Fresh%20Food%20(DFF)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20food%20venture%20that%20offers%20ready-to-eat%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(flatbread).%20Launched%20just%20last%20September%2C%20his%20business%20quickly%20gained%20traction%2C%20with%20him%20now%20selling%20a%20minimum%20of%201%2C500%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20packets%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20doing%20multiple%20menial%20jobs%20to%20starting%20own%20food%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20Class%2010%20in%202001%2C%20he%20started%20working%20as%20a%20construction%20labourer%20for%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20at%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20border%2C%20which%20earned%20him%20Rs%201%2C200%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiscontented%20with%20the%20job%2C%20he%20quit%20in%20a%20year%20and%20moved%20to%20Meghalaya%20to%20work%20in%20a%20coal%20mine.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20in%20coal%20mines%20was%20really%20very%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20blasting%20operations%20often%20induce%20ground%20vibration%20inside%20the%20mine.%20Strong%20vibrations%20damage%20the%20structure%20and%20result%20in%20ceiling%20collapse.%20We%20frequently%20witnessed%20mishaps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20it%20was%20the%20day%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaghi%20Purnima%20%3C%2Fem%3E(auspicious%20full%20moon%20day)%20when%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20from%20the%20village%20was%20inside%20the%20coal%20mine.%20Due%20to%20the%20strong%20vibrations%2C%20a%20ceiling%20collapsed%20and%20he%20got%20trapped%20inside.%20We%20later%20found%20him%20dead%3B%20his%20body%20was%20crushed%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Diganta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%