ced%20at%20Rs%2060%20and%20Rs%20100%2C%20these%20packaged%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20come%20in%20packs%20of%20five%20or%2010%20pieces.%20They%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20three%20days%2C%20which%20extends%20up%20to%20seven%20days%20if%20stored%20in%20refrigerators.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20working%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssam-based%20Akhilesh%20Gupta%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20tea%20stall%2C%20loves%20these%20parathas.%20He%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20this%20was%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20absolutely%20loved%20it.%20It%20has%20so%20many%20layers%20and%20is%20so%20soft%20to%20eat.%20We%20keep%20a%20stock%20of%20it%2C%20and%20whenever%20we%20run%20out%20of%20wheat%20at%20home%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20come%20to%20our%20rescue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Diganta%2C%20this%20experience%20helped%20him%20battle%20poverty%20and%20build%20the%20life%20he%20desired%20for%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20qualified%20enough%20to%20get%20a%20high-salaried%20job.%20I%20was%20always%20reluctant%20to%20do%20farming%2C%20so%20I%20always%20ran%20from%20city%20to%20city%20doing%20menial%20jobs.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20climb%20the%20ladder%20of%20success%20right%20from%20the%20place%20where%20it%20all%20started%20%E2%80%94%20my%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Diganta%20Das)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijrte.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fpapers%2Fv9i1%2FA2777059120.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFactors%20and%20Impact%20of%20Rural%20Out-Migration%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Publish